p%20paying%20for%20workers'%20weight-loss%20drugs.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIt%20could%20be%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20crackdown%20on%20insurance%20coverage%20of%20injections%20such%20as%20Wegovy.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDemand%20for%20weight-loss%20medications%20has%20soared%2C%20but%20employers%20and%20insurers%20say%20they%20cost%20too%20much.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EJenny%20started%20taking%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fweight-loss-obesity-drug-fda-approved-wegovy-2021-6%5C%22%3Epopular%20weight-loss%20injection%20Wegovy%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20February%20and%20saw%20results%20almost%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20appetite%20dissolved%2C%20the%20intense%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fozempic-made-cravings-food-noise-in-my-head-disappear-semaglutide-2023-4%5C%22%3Efood%20noise%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20in%20her%20head%20went%20silent%2C%20and%20she%20shed%208%20pounds%20in%20the%20first%20week.%20She%20felt%20lucky%20that%20she%20didn't%20experience%20any%20unpleasant%20side%20effects.%20Plus%2C%20Jenny%2C%20a%20nurse%20at%20Ascension%2C%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20hospital%20systems%20in%20the%20country%2C%20was%20able%20to%20get%20the%20notoriously%20expensive%20Wegovy%20for%20just%20%2425%20a%20month%20with%20her%20job-based%20insurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20her%20luck%20ran%20out%20when%20she%20went%20to%20refill%20her%20prescription%20this%20month.%20The%20pharmacy%20told%20her%20that%20instead%20of%20that%20small%20copay%2C%20Wegovy%20would%20now%20cost%20her%20an%20impossible%20%241%2C600%20a%20month%2C%20she%20said.%20Insider%20is%20identifying%20Jenny%20by%20her%20first%20name%20to%20protect%20her%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20was%20that%20Ascension%20had%20joined%20the%20league%20of%20companies%20refusing%20to%20pay%20for%20their%20employees'%20weight-loss%20prescriptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%2C%20private%20insurers%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-medicare-coverage-weight-loss-drugs-wegovy-2023-7%5C%22%3Egovernment%20programs%20such%20as%20Medicare%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0are%20facing%20immense%20pressure%20from%20patients%2C%20drugmakers%2C%20doctors%2C%20and%20obesity%20advocacy%20organizations%20to%20open%20up%20access%20to%20the%20new%20and%20effective%20weight-loss%20drugs%20that%20have%20become%20household%20names%20in%20the%20past%20year.%20But%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwill-company-health-insurance-pay-weight-loss-drugs-ozempic-wegovy-2023-6%5C%22%3Eemployers%20and%20insurers%20say%20the%20cost%20of%20covering%20the%20drugs%20will%20tank%20their%20budgets%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20eat%20into%20their%20profits%2C%20and%20drive%20up%20health-insurance%20premiums%20for%20everybody.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225616%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20boxes%20of%20Wegovy%20on%20a%20light%20wood%20counter%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ad919a8ed31300199e78af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223744%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3Epicture%20alliance%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20crackdown%20on%20insurance%20coverage%20for%20weight-loss%20drugs%20may%20be%20just%20beginning.%20Companies%20that%20provide%20health%20coverage%20to%20their%20workers%20are%20making%20decisions%20right%20now%20about%20which%20benefits%20they'll%20pay%20for%20in%202024%2C%20and%20they're%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femployers-grappling-cost-coverage-ozempic-wegovy-weight-loss-drugs-2023-2%5C%22%3Ewrestling%20with%20what%20to%20do%20about%20weight-loss%20drugs%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20their%20exorbitant%20price%20tags.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERenee%20Rayburg%2C%20a%20consultant%20at%20Pharmaceutical%20Strategies%20Group%20who%20helps%20companies%20manage%20their%20spending%20on%20prescription%20drugs%2C%20said%20she%20hadn't%20seen%20many%20employers%20retreat%20completely%20from%20covering%20weight-loss%20drugs%2C%20as%20Ascension%20is%20doing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20she%20said%20a%20couple%20of%20other%20companies%20PSG%20worked%20with%20had%20already%20scaled%20back%20their%20coverage%20of%20the%20medications.%20One%20company%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20began%20restricting%20the%20drugs%20to%20only%20people%20with%20a%20body-mass%20index%20of%20at%20least%2035%2C%20she%20said%2C%20even%20though%20some%20drugs%20are%20approved%20to%20treat%20people%20with%20less-severe%20obesity%20or%20those%20who%20are%20overweight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20hospital%20system%20and%20a%20university%20are%20stripping%20workers%20of%20their%20Wegovy%20coverage%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222100%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22man%20injecting%20ozempic%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F641db740b7834100191b17a4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221181%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20online%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmysmarthealth.org%2Fpharmacy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enotice%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ascension's%20health%20plan%20for%20employees%20began%20excluding%20expensive%20shots%20such%20as%20Wegovy%2C%20as%20well%20as%20cheaper%20anti-obesity%20pills%2C%20from%20coverage%20on%20July%201.%20That%20means%20workers%20and%20their%20dependents%20must%20shoulder%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20prescriptions%20themselves%2C%20or%20look%20for%20a%20coupon%20from%20a%20drugmaker%2C%C2%A0the%20notice%20said.%20Any%20weight-loss%20drugs%20that%20hit%20the%20market%20in%20the%20future%20would%20also%20be%20excluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAscension%20did%20not%20comment%20on%20or%20answer%20questions%20about%20what%20drove%20its%20benefit%20to%20change.%20The%20healthcare%20provider%2C%20which%20operates%20hospitals%20in%2019%20states%2C%20employs%20nearly%20140%2C000%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20University%20of%20Texas%20System%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20laid%20out%20exactly%20why%20it%20would%20stop%20paying%20for%20Wegovy%20and%20another%2C%20less-effective%20weight-loss%20drug%2C%20Saxenda%2C%20starting%20in%20September.%20This%20month%2C%20it%20told%20workers%20that%20its%20costs%20for%20the%20prescriptions%20skyrocketed%20to%20%245%20million%20a%20month%20in%20May%20from%20about%20%241.5%20million%20a%20month%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20drugs%20cost%20the%20UT%20System's%20health%20plans%20more%20than%20medications%20used%20to%20treat%20cancer%2C%20and%20continuing%20to%20pay%20for%20them%20would%20cost%20the%20plans%20an%20extra%20%2473%20million%20a%20year%20and%20drive%20up%20premiums%20by%202.5%25%20to%203%25%20for%20all%20employees%2C%20UT%20said.%20A%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20university%20system%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221993%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Headshot%20of%20Dr.%20Angela%20Fitch%2C%20the%20associate%20director%20of%20the%20Massachusetts%20General%20Hospital%20Weight%20Center%20and%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Obesity%20Medicine%20Association.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64bacbb5006a5e00194a4a02%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221495%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDr.%20Angela%20Fitch%2C%20a%20cofounder%20of%20Knownwell%20and%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Obesity%20Medicine%20Association.%3Cp%3EObesity%20Medicine%20Association%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Angela%20Fitch%2C%20a%20cofounder%20of%20the%20weight-management%20startup%20Knownwell%20and%20the%20president%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fobesitymedicine.org%2F%5C%22%3EObesity%20Medicine%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20she%20feared%20more%20companies%20would%20scale%20back%20their%20coverage%20of%20weight-loss%20drugs%20because%20of%20high%20costs%2C%20which%20would%20leave%20only%20wealthy%20people%20or%20those%20who%20work%20for%20employers%20with%20generous%20benefits%20able%20to%20afford%20the%20prescription%20obesity%20treatments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20literally%20setting%20ourselves%20back%20like%2010%20years%20because%20of%20cost%2C%26quot%3B%20Fitch%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ECompanies%20don't%20want%20to%20pay%20for%20weight-loss%20drugs%20because%20of%20high%20costs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDemand%20for%20a%20new%20class%20of%20drugs%20known%20as%20GLP-1%20agonists%20has%20surged%20in%20the%20past%20year%20or%20so%2C%20following%20the%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration's%20approval%20of%20Novo%20Nordisk's%20Wegovy%20in%20June%202021.%20Similar%20drugs%20include%20Ozempic%2C%20also%20from%20Novo%20Nordisk%2C%20and%20Eli%20Lilly's%20Mounjaro.%20Ozempic%20and%20Mounjaro%20are%20approved%20to%20treat%20type%202%20diabetes%20only%2C%20but%20doctors%20can%20prescribe%20them%20%26quot%3Boff%20label%26quot%3B%20to%20help%20with%20weight%20loss.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%205.6%20million%20prescriptions%20were%20written%20for%20GLP-1%20drugs%20for%20people%20without%20diabetes%20in%20the%20first%20five%20months%20of%202023%2C%20compared%20with%207%20million%20prescriptions%20for%20all%20of%202022%20and%202.8%20million%20in%202021%2C%20according%20to%20the%20data-analytics%20company%20Komodo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222501%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hand%20reaching%20out%20to%20a%20semaglutide%20injection%20that%20fades%20in%20and%20out%20of%20a%20black%20background%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6478f58d30404300183aa775%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221251%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGetty%3B%20Marianne%20Ayala%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20even%20as%20prescriptions%20mount%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwill-company-health-insurance-pay-weight-loss-drugs-ozempic-wegovy-2023-6%5C%22%3Einsurance%20coverage%20of%20the%20drugs%20is%20spotty%20and%20not%20improving%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20survey%20by%20the%20Pharmaceutical%20Strategies%20Group%2C%20which%20helps%20companies%20design%20their%20pharmacy%20benefits%2C%20found%20that%2041%25%20of%20employers%20polled%20covered%20weight-loss%20medications%20for%20their%20workers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETracy%20Spencer%2C%20a%20leader%20in%20the%20consultancy%20Aon's%20pharmacy%20practice%2C%20said%20many%20of%20the%20employers%20covering%20weight-loss%20drugs%20today%20were%20doing%20so%20based%20on%20a%20prior%20decision%20to%20cover%20older%2C%20lower-cost%20obesity%20medication.%20Some%20of%20these%20companies%20didn't%20even%20realize%20they%20were%20paying%20for%20expensive%20options%20such%20as%20Wegovy%20until%20they%20discovered%20that%20their%20costs%20had%20increased.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20companies%20are%20considering%20new%20ways%20to%20ensure%20that%20only%20people%20who%20qualify%20for%20GLP-1%20drugs%20get%20them%2C%20and%20some%20are%20looking%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fomada-strategy-weight-loss-drugs-semaglutide-ozempic-2023-5%5C%22%3Erequiring%20their%20workers%20on%20weight-loss%20drugs%20to%20participate%20in%20behavioral-change%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20diet%2C%20and%20exercise%20programs%2C%20Spencer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20of%20covering%20the%20drugs%20is%20the%20biggest%20issue.%20The%20shots%20have%20high%20price%20tags%20%E2%80%94%20they%20typically%20range%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.goodrx.com%2Fclasses%2Fglp-1-agonists%5C%22%3E%24900%20to%20%241%2C300%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20month%20%E2%80%94%20and%20people%20likely%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-long-do-you-have-to-take-ozempic-probably-forever-2023-6%5C%22%3Emust%20take%20them%20long-term%20to%20sustain%20weight%20loss%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Plus%2C%20many%20people%20could%20qualify%20to%20take%20them%20%E2%80%94%20about%2042%25%20of%20American%20adults%20have%20obesity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrugmakers%20insist%20that%20companies%20could%20save%20money%20by%20covering%20the%20drugs%20because%20the%20weight%20loss%20spurred%20by%20the%20injections%20would%20help%20their%20workers%20avoid%20grave%2C%20costly%20problems%20such%20as%20heart%20attacks.%20But%20insurers%20and%20employers%20say%20there's%20no%20evidence%20for%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20University%20of%20Texas%20System%20said%20as%20much%20to%20its%20workers.%20Its%20health%20plans%20haven't%20seen%20reduced%20costs%20for%20other%20health%20conditions%20from%20the%203%2C100%20plan%20members%20using%20Wegovy%20or%20Saxenda%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20savings%20are%20not%20being%20realized%20due%20to%20the%20excessive%20cost%20the%20drug%20manufacturer%20charges%20for%20the%20weight%20loss%20medication%2C%26quot%3B%20UT%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20UT%20System%20added%20that%20less%20than%20half%20of%20its%20members%20who%20were%20prescribed%20the%20drugs%20kept%20taking%20them.%20Patients%20who%20stop%20taking%20drugs%20like%20Wegovy%20can%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F35441470%2F%5C%22%3Eregain%20some%20or%20all%20of%20the%20weight%20they%20lost%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EChanging%20jobs%20to%20get%20Wegovy%20coverage%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJenny%2C%20the%20Ascension%20nurse%2C%20said%20she's%20desperate%20to%20keep%20taking%20Wegovy%20and%20disappointed%20that%20a%20hospital%20system%20that%20promoted%20getting%20and%20staying%20healthy%20would%20take%20away%20something%20that%20helped%20her%20do%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20February%2C%20she's%20gone%20from%20215%20pounds%20to%20180.%20Her%20blood%20pressure%20and%20cholesterol%20levels%20have%20improved%2C%20her%20back%20and%20joints%20don't%20ache%20as%20much%2C%20and%20she%20generally%20feels%20better%20about%20herself%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Ascension%20wouldn't%20pay%20for%20her%20latest%20Wegovy%20refill%2C%20she%20found%20a%20Novo%20Nordisk%20coupon%20that%20helped%20lower%20her%20cost%20to%20%24900%20at%20the%20pharmacy%20counter%2C%20but%20that's%20not%20a%20price%20she%20can%20afford%20to%20pay%20every%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20she's%20even%20considering%20finding%20a%20new%20employer%20that%20would%20pay%20for%20the%20drug%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20means%20that%20much%20to%20me%20that%20I'm%20willing%20to%20change%20jobs%20for%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femployers-stop-covering-weight-loss-drugs-due-cost-price-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690025400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64baccd0006a5e00194a4d85%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femployers-stop-covering-weight-loss-drugs-due-cost-price-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Employers%20are%20balking%20at%20the%20high%20cost%20of%20new%2C%20effective%20weight-loss%20drugs%20like%20Wegovy%2C%20which%20usually%20range%20in%20price%20from%20%24900%20to%20%241%2C300%20a%20month.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22slivingston%40businessinsider.com%20(Shelby%20Livingston)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femployers-stop-covering-weight-loss-drugs-due-cost-price-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meet%20a%2064-year-old%20San%20Francisco%20Uber%20driver%20who%20says%20switching%20to%20a%20Tesla%20has%20saved%20him%20more%20than%20%241%2C000%20a%20month%20on%20gas%20and%20maintenance%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225411%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tesla%20charging%20at%20Supercharger%20in%20Pleasanton%2C%20California.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64074f9e934c2c001802de86%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222705%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20different%20Tesla%20being%20charged.%3Cp%3ESmith%20Collection%2FGado%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E64-year-old%20Uber%20driver%20Wesley%20Johnson%20started%20driving%20a%20rented%20Tesla%20four%20months%20ago.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EHe%20said%20he's%20saving%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20on%20gas%20and%20has%20no%20plans%20to%20turn%20back.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EJohnson%20also%20offered%20tips%20for%20Uber%20drivers%20looking%20to%20make%20the%20electric-vehicle%20switch.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWesley%20Johnson%2C%2064%2C%20uses%20the%20income%20he%20earns%20as%20a%20San%20Francisco%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-eats-driver-how-to-get-good-tips-stay-safe-2023-5%5C%22%3EUber%20driver%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20offer%20some%20financial%20support%20to%20his%20four%20children%20and%20seven%20grandchildren.%20He%20says%20switching%20to%20a%20Tesla%20will%20help%20him%20pull%20in%20more%20money%20over%20time%20by%20reducing%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%20is%20semi-retired%20but%20told%20Insider%20he%20drives%20roughly%2040%20hours%20per%20week%20for%20Uber%20%E2%80%94%2012%20hours%20Thursday%20through%20Saturday%2C%20and%20four%20hours%20on%20Sunday.%20He's%20brought%20in%20more%20than%20%2450%2C000%20in%20revenue%20over%20the%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20documents%20viewed%20by%20Insider.%20But%20being%20a%20driver%20also%20means%20paying%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnyc-uber-driver-gas-prices-make-it-hard-pay-bills-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egas%20and%20vehicle%20maintenance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20can%20add%20up%20and%20eat%20into%20take-home%20profits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20extra%20expenses%20are%20why%20Johnson%20%E2%80%94%20who's%20completed%20over%2019%2C000%20trips%20since%202014%20and%20has%20a%204.96%20rating%20%E2%80%94%20was%20intrigued%20when%20he%20heard%20about%20Uber's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C