as%20to%20do%20it%20once%20when%20he%20works%20his%2012-hour%20days.%20He%20said%20he's%20also%20taken%20advantage%20of%20another%20Uber%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fuber.enroll.evgo.com%2F%3Fuclick_id%3D5185daf0-0d1d-4819-bce5-88b821db2383%26utm_campaign%3Dretail%2520program%26utm_medium%3Demail%26utm_source%3Duber%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epartnership%20with%20EVgo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20provides%20eligible%20drivers%20with%20discounted%20charging%20rates.%20Uber%20wants%20all%20of%20its%20North%20American%20vehicles%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-electric-vehicles-evs-sustainability-charging-anxiety-dara-khosrowshahi-2023-6%5C%22%3Eelectric%20by%202030%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222316%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22wesley%20johnson%20uber%20driver%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64bacabf03c40c001a982b4f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221737%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWesley%20Johnson%2C%2064%2C%20says%20he's%20saved%20roughly%20%241%2C400%20per%20month%20on%20gas%20since%20switching%20to%20an%20electric%20vehicle.%3Cp%3EWesley%20Johnson%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20cites%20Uber's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uber.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Fdrive%2Fservices%2Felectric%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ezero%20emissions%20incentive%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20which%20pays%20him%20an%20extra%20%241%20per%20ride%20(up%20to%20%244%2C000%20per%20year)%20until%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2Fuber-under-the-hood%2Funderstanding-upfront-fares-491cbaf975d6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJanuary%20of%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20as%20a%20financial%20incentive%20for%20driving%20electric.%20He%20said%20he%20typically%20averages%20about%20120%20trips%20per%20week%2C%20which%20he%20views%20as%20%24120%20dollars%20he%20can%20use%20to%20put%20towards%20his%20rental%20payment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20my%20mind%2C%20I'm%20only%20coming%20out%20of%20pocket%20like%20a%20few%20hundred%20dollars%20a%20week%2C%20plus%20the%20charge%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20how%20I%20look%20at%20it%20%E2%80%94%20I%20take%20that%20money%20to%20use%20towards%20paying%20for%20the%20car.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20advantage%20to%20Hertz's%20EV%20program%20is%20drivers%20who%20rent%20through%20the%20company%20face%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D329f16586515d1743745b07789f18ddd3427b8acf754cfb671c417bf28797b2a%26postID%3D64b99b77a3dc3f73b838cfb3%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.hertz.com%252Frentacar%252Fmisc%252Findex.jsp%253FtargetPage%253Duber_landing_page.jsp%2526LinkType%253DHZLK%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eno%20maintenance%20costs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Johnson%20drives%20so%20much%20%E2%80%94%20by%20his%20count%2C%20he's%20logged%2045%2C000%20in%20his%20EV%20since%20March%20%E2%80%94%20he%20prefers%20not%20to%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20the%20wear%20and%20tear%20he's%20putting%20on%20his%20vehicle.%20He%20recalls%20spending%20thousands%20of%20dollars%20repairing%20his%20Mercedes%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there's%20a%20tradeoff%20to%20all%20these%20savings.%20Johnson%20said%20he%20pays%20%24410%20per%20week%20%E2%80%94%20%241%2C640%20per%20month%20%E2%80%94%20to%20rent%20his%20long-range%20EV%2C%20significantly%20more%20than%20his%20Mercedes%20payment.%20He%20also%20hasn't%20seen%20a%20material%20difference%20in%20revenue%20from%20Uber%20rides%20since%20he%20switched%20to%20the%20Tesla.%20What%20he's%20banking%20on%20is%20the%20cost%20cuts%20in%20other%20areas%20combining%20in%20the%20long%20run%20to%20create%20a%20net-positive%20situation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20it%20just%20makes%20more%20sense%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnson%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20spend%20a%20little%20more%20money%2C%20but%20at%20the%20end%20of%20it%2C%20it's%20less%20mental%20stress%20on%20you%20about%20your%20car%20breaking%20down.%20Stuff%20happens.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20another%20perk%20that's%20made%20driving%20the%20EV%20worth%20it%20for%20Johnson%3A%20he%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-driver-tipping-trends-getting-worse-taylor-swift-riders-best-2023-4%5C%22%3Ecustomer%20tips%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20a%20bit%20better%20since%20he%20started%20driving%20a%20Tesla.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20people%2C%20they%20like%20the%20Tesla%2C%20that%20new%20Tesla%20feeling.%20And%20they%20say%2C%20'Oh%2C%20my%20first%20time%20riding%20a%20Tesla%2C'%20stuff%20like%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20some%20EV%20rides%20also%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uber.com%2Fus%2Fen%2Fdrive%2Fservices%2Fcomfort-electric%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigher%20fares%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20in%20theory%20makes%20it%20possible%20for%20drivers%20like%20Johnson%20to%20earn%20more%20per%20ride.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Uber%20drivers%20should%20know%20before%20making%20the%20EV%20switch%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%20has%20a%20few%20tips%20for%20any%20Uber%20drivers%20who%20are%20considering%20renting%20or%20buying%20an%20EV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20he%20said%20it's%20important%20to%20establish%20an%20optimal%20charging%20routine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohnson%20said%20it's%20less%20expensive%20to%20charge%20his%20car%20during%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-charge-your-electric-car-at-home-2023-5%5C%22%3Eoff-peak%20hours%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20he%20tends%20to%20charge%20his%20vehicle%20late%20in%20the%20evening%20as%20a%20result%2C%20typically%20when%20the%20car's%20battery%20is%20around%2020%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20charging%20takes%20roughly%2040%20minutes%2C%20and%20that%20the%20lengthy%20charge%20time%20is%20a%20big%20reason%20he%20opted%20for%20the%20long-range%20Tesla.%20This%20allows%20him%20to%20charge%20just%20once%20per%20day%20%E2%80%94%20ideally%20at%20the%20end%20of%20his%20workday%20%E2%80%94%20and%20avoid%20cutting%20into%20too%20much%20of%20his%20driving%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20Johnson%20said%20drivers%20should%20be%20conscious%20of%20where%20their%20trips%20take%20them.%20He%20tries%20to%20avoid%20trips%20that%20take%20him%20on%20the%20freeway%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20because%20the%20car's%20battery%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kbb.com%2Fcar-advice%2Fev-battery-drain%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3D%25E2%2580%259CSteady%2520driving%2520at%2520highway%2520speed%2Cbattery%2520when%2520coasting%2520and%2520braking.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeclines%20more%20quickly%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20faster%20he%20drives.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThird%2C%20he%20said%20drivers%20should%20make%20sure%20they're%20willing%20to%20drive%20consistently.%20Per%20his%20Uber-Hertz%20rental%20agreement%2C%20Johnson%20said%20he%20has%20to%20do%20a%20minimum%20of%2030%20trips%20per%20week%20to%20keep%20the%20car.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoing%20forward%2C%20Johnson%20said%20he%20plans%20to%20keep%20renting%20his%20EV%20for%20the%20foreseeable%20future.%20In%20addition%20to%20saving%20money%20to%20support%20his%20family%2C%20he%20said%20he%20has%20one%20other%20goal%20in%20mind.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to%20have%20one%20of%20these%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20the%20Tesla.%20%26quot%3BI%20could%20cut%20down%20that%20%241%2C600%20rental%20expense%20that%20I%20pay%20for%20it.%20I%20put%20money%20towards%20saving%20for%20one%20of%20these.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-green-rent-tesla-save-money-ridehail-budgeting-gig-work