t-3.55.06-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUjjain%20(Madhya%20Pradesh)%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Two%20separate%20videos%20from%20the%20Chhatri%20Chowk%20area%20of%20Ujjain%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media%20on%20July%2017%2C%20with%20claims%20that%20three%20Muslim%20boys%20in%20the%20videos%20were%20spitting%20on%20the%20passing%20%E2%80%9CMahakal%20Ki%20Sawari%E2%80%9D%20Procession.%20The%20widely%20shared%20videos%20shot%20by%20men%20who%20were%20part%20of%20the%20Mahakal%20Yatra%20led%20to%20the%20arrest%20of%20three%20accused%2C%20including%20two%20minors%2C%20and%20the%20demolition%20of%20their%20residence.%20Drums%20and%20DJ%20music%20were%20played%20during%20the%20demolition%2C%20a%20new%20addition%20to%20the%20phenomenon%20of%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fconstitutional-conduct-group-cji-nv-ramana-bulldozer-justice%5C%22%3Ebulldozer%20justice%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9C.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kharakua%20police%20station%20registered%20a%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20against%20three%20unknown%20accused%20under%20various%20offences%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC)%2C%20including%20deliberate%20acts%20to%20outrage%20religious%20feelings%2C%20offences%20in%20a%20place%20of%20worship%20and%20disturbing%20a%20religious%20assembly.%20The%20complainant%2C%20Sawan%20Lot%2C%20stated%20in%20the%20FIR%20that%20the%20entire%20incident%20was%20recorded%20by%20Indore%20resident%20Masoom%20Jaiswal%20on%20his%20phone.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20incident%20has%20deeply%20hurt%20my%20religious%20sentiments%20and%20the%20entire%20society.%20We%20demand%20appropriate%20action%20in%20the%20matter%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ujjain%20police%20arrested%20three%20individuals%2C%20including%20two%20minors%20and%20an%2018-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20with%20Akbar%20Hussain%2C%20the%20uncle%20of%20two%20of%20the%20accused%20individuals.%20Hussain%20and%20two%20of%20his%20brothers%20ran%20a%20shop%20and%20resided%20with%20their%20families%20in%20the%20same%20house%20%E2%80%93%20which%20was%20demolished%20by%20the%20authorities.%20When%20this%20reporter%20reached%20him%2C%20Hussain%20was%20busy%20clearing%20the%20debris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETracing%20the%20events%20of%20July%2017%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHussain%20recalled%20the%20evening%20of%20July%2017.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20administration%20ordered%20all%20shops%20to%20be%20shut%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9CMahakal%20Ki%20Sawari%E2%80%9D%20procession.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20went%20inside%20our%20home%20to%20rest%20and%20the%20kids%20to%20the%20neighbouring%20terrace.%20A%20few%20men%20from%20the%20procession%20shot%20their%20purported%20videos%20and%20began%20protesting%20outside%20the%20Kharakua%20police%20station.%20Ignorant%20of%20what%20was%20happening%2C%20we%20reopened%20the%20shop%20when%20the%20Yatra%20passed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Kharakua%20police%20station%20is%20only%20a%20minute%E2%80%99s%20distance%20from%20our%20home.%20It%20is%20normal%20to%20hear%20protests%20and%20sloganeering%20there.%20A%20few%20policemen%20came%20to%20our%20shop%20after%20maghrib%20prayer%20and%20identified%20our%20kids.%20We%20inquired%20about%20what%20happened.%20They%20informed%20me%20that%20my%20kids%20spat%20at%20the%20yatra.%20We%20are%20on%20good%20terms%20with%20the%20policemen.%20They%20often%20sit%20at%20our%20shop.%20When%20the%20policeman%20said%20that%20%E2%80%98sahab%E2%80%99%20has%20summoned%20our%20kids%2C%20we%20sent%20them%20without%20hesitation%20and%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20bother%20to%20accompany%20them%20thinking%20that%20they%20will%20return%20after%20a%20minor%20reprimand%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Hussain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continued%20that%20the%20situation%20at%20the%20police%20station%20was%20dire.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20still%20relaxed%20at%20our%20shop%20working%20without%20doubting%20that%20it%20might%20be%20due%20to%20our%20kids.%20We%20closed%20our%20shop%20as%20soon%20we%20realised%20the%20context%20of%20chaos.%20Our%20kids%20were%20taken%20into%20custody%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20were%20arrested%20and%20their%20bail%20was%20declined%20the%20next%20day.%20%E2%80%9CEven%20the%20advocate%20advised%20us%20to%20be%20patient%20to%20avoid%20any%20unwanted%20situation.%20We%20agreed%20on%20it%20to%20maintain%20communal%20harmony%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Hussain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20viral%20video%20narrative%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkbar%20Hussain%20dismissed%20any%20allegations%20that%20the%20kids%20spat%20at%20the%20yatra.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20Hindu%20procession%20passes%20from%20their%20area%20every%20year%20and%20they%20wholeheartedly%20welcome%20it.%20One%20video%20accuses%20the%20kids%20of%20spitting%20from%20a%20neighbouring%20terrace.%20%E2%80%9CA%20kid%20has%20a%20habit%20of%20spitting.%20There%20is%20a%20vast%20green%20color%20shade%20in%20front%20of%20the%20house%20preventing%20the%20spit%20from%20reaching%20the%20road.%20It%20may%20have%20resembled%20spitting%20on%20procession%20but%20that%20is%20not%20true.%20They%20could%20not%20prove%20it.%20The%20video%20in%20which%20a%20boy%20is%20standing%20in%20a%20blue%20shirt%20with%20a%20water%20bottle%20is%20from%20our%20gallery%2C%20which%20was%20later%20made%20the%20basis%20for%20the%20demolition.%20Does%20it%20look%20clear%20from%20the%20video%20that%20the%20boy%20was%20spitting%3F%20Those%20children%20are%20too%20young.%20They%20haven%E2%80%99t%20seen%20anything%2C%E2%80%9D%20stated%20Hussain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FUjjain%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Ujjain%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E0%A4%87%E0%A4%B2%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%9C%E