n%20those%20opportunities.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESam%20Farber%20doesn't%20want%20to%20be%20the%20smartest%20person%20in%20the%20room.%20But%20if%20he's%20working%20from%20his%20bedroom%2C%20that's%20inevitable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%20Farber%20is%20excited%20to%20start%20his%20first%20full-time%20job%20next%20month.%20It'll%20be%20in%20person%20five%20days%20a%20week%20at%20JPMorgan%20in%20Chicago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFarber%2C%2022%2C%20wants%20to%20learn%20from%20older%20colleagues%20%E2%80%94%20by%20sitting%20in%20on%20phone%20calls%2C%20listening%20to%20presentations%2C%20and%20grabbing%20coffee%20with%20execs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20JPMorgan%2C%20you're%20probably%20never%20going%20to%20be%20the%20smartest%20person%20in%20the%20room%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that's%20a%20great%20thing%20%E2%80%94%20when%20you're%20able%20to%20absorb%20from%20so%20many%20smart%20individuals.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFarber%20is%20one%20of%20many%20Gen%20Zers%20excited%20to%20work%20IRL%2C%20in%20part%2C%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shrm.org%2Fresourcesandtools%2Fhr-topics%2Forganizational-and-employee-development%2Fpages%2Fgeneration-z-seeks-guidance-in-the-workplace.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Estudy%20colleagues%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20who've%20grown%20up%20in%20the%20business.%20The%20trouble%20is%2C%20those%20more-senior%20people%20aren't%20always%20around.%20Established%20workers%20who%20ghost%20the%20office%20often%20find%20that%20skipping%20the%20commute%20benefits%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fback-to-office-killing-morale-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Equality%20of%20life%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0giving%20them%20time%20for%20things%20such%20as%20taking%20care%20of%20kids.%20But%20these%20people's%20work-from-home%2