nishments%20to%20all%20those%20involved%20culprits.%20That%20unfortunate%20incident%20at%20occurred%20at%20B%20Phainom%20village%20under%20Kangpokpi%20district%20truly%20manifested%20unspeakable%20crime%20against%20women%20which%20continues%20to%20amplify%20the%20present%20crisis%20and%20plague%20Manipur%2C%E2%80%9D%20Newmai%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9DThe%20Naga%20MLAs%20forum%20also%20extended%20its%20sincere%20solidarity%20to%20those%20victims%20and%20family%20members%20who%20were%20traumatised%20and%20pained%20while%20extending%20condolences%20to%20those%20bereaved%20family%20members%20of%20those%20killed%20in%20the%20sad%20incident%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeaders%20of%20the%20Naga%20community%20have%20largely%20maintained%20silence%20over%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20between%20the%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20communities.%20While%20Naga%20student%20groups%20were%20part%20of%20the%20solidarity%20march%20that%20has%20been%20seen%20as%20the%20spark%20that%20lit%20the%20fire%2C%20the%20community%20has%20largely%20been%20unaffected%20by%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fmanipur-naga-mlas-crimes-unacceptable-tomorrow-may-be-naga-women-8853254%2F%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20five%20of%20the%20MLAs%20are%20from%20the%20Naga%20People%E2%80%99s%20Front%20(NPF)%20and%20two%20from%20%C2%A0the%20National%20People%E2%80%99s%20Party%20(NPP)%2C%20both%20of%20which%20are%20BJP%20allies.%20There%20were%20also%20two%20BJP%20MLAs%20and%20an%20Independent%20MLA%20who%20signed%20the%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNone%20of%20us%20had%20seen%20the%20video%20till%20Wednesday%2C%20and%20it%20was%20a%20shock.%20We%20had%20heard%20rumours%20of%20cases%20of%20rape%20and%20molestation%20of%20women%2C%20but%20this%20was%20the%20first%20proof%20we%20saw.%20It%20is%20not%20possible%20for%20any%20human%20being%20to%20carry%20out%20such%20a%20heinous%20crime%20%E2%80%93%20they%20were%20animals.%20No%20matter%20what%20the%20misunderstanding%20between%20the%20two%20communities%20are%2C%20even%20in%20times%20of%20war%2C%20you%20cannot%20make%20women%20the%20collateral%20damage%2C%E2%80%99%E2%80%99%20Newmai%20told%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20while%20the%20Naga%20community%20may%20not%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20clashes%20it%20is%20affected.%20%E2%80%9CLife%20has%20come%20to%20a%20standstill%20and%20normalcy%20no%20longer%20exists%20in%20the%20state.%20Soon%20after%20the%20violence%20erupted%2C%20we%20Naga%20MLAs%20formed%20peace%20committees%20and%20tried%20reaching%20out%20to%20both%20communities%20to%20get%20them%20to%20the%20table%20for%20discussions.%20But%20this%20has%20not%20really%20been%20successful%20so%20far.%20Even%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20two%20communities%20are%20trying%20their%20best%20to%20restore%20peace%2C%20but%20they%20are%20unable%20to%20control%20the%20public.%20The%20situation%20has%20spiralled%20out%20of%20control%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20unnamed%20Naga%20leader%20told%20the%20newspaper%20that%20the%20violence%20is%20continuing%20because%20%E2%80%9Cone%20man%20is%20being%20protected%E2%80%9D.%20The%20leader%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20can%E2%80%99t%20understand%20why%20the%20Centre%20is%20shielding%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20(N%20Biren%20Singh).%20There%20are%20over%2030%20MLAs%20in%20the%20BJP.%20Many%20of%20these%20leaders%20are%20highly%20respected%20in%20the%20communities%20and%20have%20a%20clean%20record.%20Why%20can%E2%80%99t%20the%20Central%20leadership%20just%20change%20the%20CM%3F%E2%80%99%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690017681000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F20222528%2Fimage-1149.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fall-10-naga-mlas-