20to%20a%20big%20music%20company%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224584%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amman%20Ahmed%2C%20second%20from%20right%2C%20with%20Create%20Music%20Group's%20executive%20team.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b90e79a46ce30019a26cc5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223438%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAmman%20Ahmed%2C%20second%20from%20right%2C%20with%20Create%20Music%20Group's%20executive%20team.%3Cp%3ECreate%20Music%20Group%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20company%20that%20creates%20music%20to%20help%20relax%20dogs%20and%20cats%20was%20acquired%20by%20an%20LA-based%20group.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMusic%20For%20Pets%20runs%20RelaxMyDog%20and%20ReleaxMyCat%20and%20was%20bought%20by%20Create%20Music%20Group%20in%20June.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20UK-based%20cofounder%20of%20Music%20For%20Pets%2C%20Amman%20Ahmed%2C%20says%20he's%20barely%20spent%20anything%20on%20marketing.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPet%20owners%20care%20a%20great%20deal%20about%20their%20furry%20friends%20and%20want%20them%20to%20be%20happy.%20Believe%20it%20or%20not%2C%20millions%20even%20tune%20in%20to%20a%20couple%20of%20YouTube%20channels%20to%20play%20music%20aimed%20at%20relaxing%20their%20dogs%20and%20cats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusic%20For%20Pets%20was%20founded%20in%20the%20UK%20more%20than%20five%20years%20ago%20and%20an%20estimated%2014.5%20million%20hours%20of%20its%20content%20is%20now%20consumed%20a%20month.%20And%20now%20the%20company's%20been%20acquired%20by%20a%20US%20music%20distribution%20and%20rights%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECofounder%20Amman%20Ahmed%20Ahmed%20had%20read%20studies%20about%20the%20link%20between%20animal%20anxiety%20and%20music%20and%20came%20up%20with%20the%20idea%20of%20starting%20a%20YouTube%20channel%20for%20pets%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20looked%20online%20for%20producers%20to%20create%20content%20and%20found%20Ricardo%20Henriquez%20who%20was%20based%20in%20El%20Salvador.%20He%20charged%20just%20%2450%20for%20his%20first%20composition%20and%20became%20the%20co-founder%20of%20Music%20For%20Pets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20VC-backed%20project%20that%20focused%20on%20music%20for%20studying%20didn't%20work%20out%2C%20Ahmed%20turned%20all%20his%20attention%20to%20pets.%20Henriquez%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20was%20inspired%20by%20his%20own%20dog's%20struggles%20with%20loud%20noises%20in%20El%20Salvador.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20some%20trial%20and%20error%2C%20they%20came%20up%20with%20a%20formula%20for%20music%20and%20images%20that%20owners%20say%20helps%20their%20pets%20relax.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20time%20Ahmed%20and%20Henriquez%20have%20worked%20together%2C%20they%20still%20haven't%20met%20face%20to%20face%20but%20plan%20to%20do%20so%20in%20Guatemala%20next%20year.%20Technology%20has%20allowed%20them%20to%20grow%20their%20audience%20into%20the%20millions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAhmed's%20YouTube%20channels%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUC2BDs0pu-C1A4POY0g9rZxw%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERelaxMyDog%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUC89zrYB2M6mj00nHdHWD-EA%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERelaxMyCat%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20become%20hugely%20popular%2C%20with%201.5%20million%20and%20800%2C000%20subscribers%20respectively.%20According%20to%20the%20profile%20page%2C%C2%A0RelaxMyDog%20offers%20music%20and%20TV%20that%20will%20help%20any%20breed%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bvariety%20of%20problems%20including%20separation%20anxiety%2C%20sleep%20problems%2C%20loneliness%2C%20boredom%20and%20depression.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FoMcvleEwamg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%2