2FH20230708134993.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIronic%20as%20it%20may%20seem%2C%20it%20has%20begun%20to%20appear%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20majoritarian%2C%20nativist%2C%20ideology%20alone%20is%20not%20proving%20sufficient%20to%20reassure%20him%20that%20in%202024%20he%20will%20be%20on%20a%20winning%20streak%20yet%20again.%20This%20is%20weighing%20down%20the%20political%20context%20for%20him%20and%20could%2C%20on%20balance%2C%20persuade%20the%20leader%20to%20go%20to%20the%20country%20sooner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20chips%20are%20not%20fully%20down%20yet%2C%20but%20the%20era%20of%20open%20optimism%20can%20now%20be%20discounted%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20now%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20total%20grasp%20with%20no%20room%20even%20for%20within-the-system%20consultation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20call%20to%20arms%20in%20the%20name%20of%20religion%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20dog%20whistle%20that%20went%20with%20it%20%E2%80%93%20was%20earlier%20enough%20to%20rally%20the%20faithful.%20In%20the%20recent%20Karnataka%20assembly%20election%2C%20however%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fchant-jai-bajrang-bali-while-casting-your-votes-modi-says-in-karnataka%5C%22%3Eonly%20trick%20Modi%20can%20summon%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20of%20no%20avail%20in%20persuading%20most%20people%20who%20are%20not%20RSS%20groupies.%20Nor%20did%20an%20appeal%20to%20communal%20sentiment%20pay%20satisfactory%20dividend%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20earlier.%20Voters%20are%20becoming%20more%20discriminating.%20They%20can%20now%20better%20see%20when%20the%20devotion%20is%20synthetic%2C%20linked%20only%20to%20keeping%20a%20hold%20on%20power%2C%20regardless%20of%20performance%20in%20office.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20there%20can%20be%20no%20doubt%20that%20Modi%20has%20left%20a%20deep%2C%20dark%2C%20imprint%20of%20his%20far-right%20ideology%20on%20the%20socio-political%20landscape%20of%20the%20country%2C%20more%20than%20any%20other%20representative%20of%20that%20belief%20system.%20In%20the%20space%20of%20nine%20years%2C%20he%20has%20fulfilled%20two%20key%20aspirations%20of%20the%20RSS-Jana%20Sangh%2C%20which%20the%20BJP%20took%20over%20as%20matters%20of%20legacy%2C%20and%20is%20on%20course%20to%20fulfil%20the%20third%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fopinion%2Fet-commentary%2Fucc-joins-article-370-ram-temple-as-key-issues-for-bjp-in-2024-elections%2Farticleshow%2F101331368.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Emake%20the%20right%20noises%20about%20it%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20pre-election%2C%20with%20a%20view%20to%20prising%20communal%20benefit%20out%20of%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELeaving%20his%20impress%20on%20the%20judiciary%20with%20indubitable%20force%2C%20Modi%20has%20ensured%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%20Showing%20unconcern%20for%20principles%20and%20procedures%2C%20his%20government%20took%20away%20the%20constitutional%20privileges%20of%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20only%20Muslim-majority%20state.%20And%20work%20has%20begun%20in%20seeming%20earnest%20to%20wrap%20up%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20(UCC)%20with%20intimations%20of%20a%20design%20that%20aims%20to%20further%20constrain%20India%E2%80%99s%20Muslims.%20The%20prime%20minister%20does%20seem%20to%20be%20in%20a%20hurry%20on%20this.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20normal%20course%2C%20this%20should%20have%20been%20the%20perfect%20background%20to%20launch%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20bid%20for%20a%20shot%20at%20the%20job%20for%20the%20third%20time%20in%20a%20row%2C%20but%20the%20script%20has%20fallen%20short.%20The%20zealot%20has%20failed%20in%20his%20life%E2%80%99s%20clearly%20stated%20fourth%20ideological%20objective%3A%20to%20drive%20the%20Congress%20party%20to%20extinction.%20This%20was%20thought%20to%20be%20a%20low-hanging%20fruit.%20But%20circumstances%20have%20conspired%20to%20produce%20the%20opposite%20result.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Congress%20grows%20in%20stride%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20stride%20has%20grown%20longer%20and%20stronger%20when%20greater%20has%20been%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20success%20on%20the%20legacy%20issues%20of%20his%20ideology.%20The%20much-advertised%20goal%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9CCongress-%3Cem%3Emukt%3C%2Fem%3E%20Bharat%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20effectively%2C%20the%20driving%20of%20the%20Congress%20into%20the%20Arabian%20Sea%20%E2%80%93%20has%20disintegrated.%20Eliminating%20the%20party%20of%20Gandhi%2C%20Patel%2C%20Nehru%2C%20Bose%20and%20Azad%20from%20the%20scene%20is%20a%20necessary%20condition%20to%20establish%20the%20sway%20of%20a%20militarised%20political%20Hindu%20order%2C%20or%20Hindutva.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20hard%20to%20miss%20the%20dialectic%20%E2%80%93%20indeed%20the%20great%20historical%20irony%20%E2%80%93%20that%20confronts%20the%20PM%20and%20his%20clique%20now.%20The%20Congress%20party%20has%20succeeded%20in%20energising%20and%20transforming%20itself%20even%20as%20the%20ideological%20agenda%20of%20the%20RSS-BJP%20was%20being%20spun%20out%20with%20messianic%20spirit%20by%20the%20man%20whose%20self-regard%20is%20that%20of%20the%20all-conquering%20emperor.%20This%20was%20not%20supposed%20to%20happen.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20poison%20feed%20of%20Hindutva%20appeared%20to%20produce%20a%20favourable%20response%20at%20first.%20The%20ranks%20of%20the%20faithful%20swelled.%20But%20when%20the%20social%20and%20economic%20logic%20produced%20in%20the%20ensuing%20turmoil%20brought%20its%20harsh%20results%20to%20a%20largely%20poor%20country%20with%20a%20syncretic%20tradition%2C%20a%20silent%20backlash%20began%20to%20emerge.%20The%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20provided%20the%20agency%20to%20tap%20the%20developing%20disenchantment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20uncanny%20grasp%20of%20the%20simmering%20discontent%20produced%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbharat-jodo-yatra-public-action-congress%5C%22%3EBharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%3C%2Fa%3E%20(BJY)%2C%20which%20neatly%20encapsulated%20two%20connected%20strands%20that%20are%20not%20always%20immediately%20obvious%20%E2%80%93%20namely%2C%20that%20in%20Indian%20conditions%2C%20building%20an%20edifice%20on%20the%20enterprise%20of%20communalism%20cannot%20but%20be%20underwritten%20by%20big%20business%2C%20and%20this%20cannot%20but%20produce%20large-scale%20unemployment%20and%20adverse%20conditions%20of%20life%20for%20ordinary%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2F07122446%2FScreenshot-2022-10-07-at-12.23.0.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2F07122446%2FScreenshot-2022-10-07-at-12.23.0.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2F07122446%2FScreenshot-2022-10-07-at-12.23.0-300x191.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F10%2F07122446%2FScreenshot-2022-10-07-at-12.23.0-1024x650.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-623181%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22762%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERahul%20Gandhi%20in%20Karnataka%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40INCIndia%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETaking%20heart%20from%20the%20BJY%2C%20the%20Congress%20party%20has%20in%20quick%20time%20sought%20to%20re-order%20much%20of%20the%20scatter%20that%20had%20earlier%20characterised%20it.%20Party%20elections%20have%20produced%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmallikarjun-kharge-shows-his-mettle-and-guile-in-parliament%5C%22%3Eoutstanding%20leader%20as%20the%20president%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20two%20state%20elections%20have%20been%20won%20on%20the%20trot%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZX9tIUjNjVk%5C%22%3Edissidence%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20key%20states%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Frajasthan-polls-sachin-pilot-buries-hatchet-with-ashok-gehlot-2403814-2023-07-08%5C%22%3Eaddressed%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20a%20governance%20agenda%20focusing%20on%20the%20underprivileged%20has%20been%20rolled%20out%20in%20party-run%20states.%20And%20this%20is%20producing%20a%20demonstration%20effect%20nationwide.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EImportantly%2C%20in%20addition%2C%20the%20Congress%20seems%20to%20be%20embracing%20a%20new%20spirit.%20This%20looks%20to%20have%20three%20strands%3A%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20segments%20that%20are%20bearing%20the%20brunt%20of%20Modi-era%20policies%20and%20politics%20and%20on%20that%20basis%20seek%20to%20re-construct%20a%20key%20social%20force%20as%20a%20challenge%20to%20communal%20politics%3B%20to%20seek%20to%20connect%20with%20opposition%20parties%20in%20a%20wide%20arc%20in%20spite%20of%20some%20serious%20contradictions%3B%20and%20consciously%20link%20to%20dozens%20of%20social%20organisations%20and%20voluntary%20agencies%20across%20the%20country%2C%20many%20rooted%20in%20the%20legacy%20of%20Gandhian%20civil%20resistance%2C%20with%20offshoots%20connecting%20to%20Lohia%20and%20Jayaprakash.%20The%20value%20of%20these%20and%20their%20effort%20was%20underlined%20in%20the%20recent%20ouster%20of%20BJP%20rule%20in%20Karnataka.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECentre%E2%80%99s%20reputation%20in%20disarray%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20performance%20and%20reputation%20are%20in%20disarray.%20After%20adjusting%20for%20inflation%2C%20the%20much-touted%20growth%20rate%2C%20which%20the%20worshipful%20media%20sections%20love%20to%20talk%20up%2C%20is%20well%20below%20par%20and%20hitting%20tens%20of%20millions%20very%20hard.%20Unlike%20key%20major%20economies%2C%20India%20has%20not%20yet%20recovered%20to%20pre-COVID%20rates%20of%20growth%20%E2%80%93%20which%20were%20already%20depressed%20on%20account%20of%20demonetisation%20and%20faulty%20GST%20rollout.%20On%20the%20security%20side%2C%20large%20chunks%20of%20territory%20in%20Ladakh%20are%20under%20China%E2%80%99s%20occupation%20and%20the%20government%20seems%20too%20scared%20to%20say%20so%20outright.%20The%20wide%20and%20dark%20misuse%20of%20the%20CBI%20and%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20against%20opponents%20is%20a%20subject%20of%20discussion%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20small%20border%20state%20of%20Manipur%20is%20on%20fire%2C%20the%20social%20fabric%20has%20been%20torn%20asunder%2C%20and%20the%20government%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20backing%20one%20side%20on%20a%20communal%20basis.%20Regime%20supporters%20have%20burned%20more%20than%20300%20churches%20without%20being%20afraid%20of%20advertising%20their%20anti-Christian%20attitude.%20The%20recent%20exposure%20of%20how%20those%20in%20authority%20have%20permitted%20open%2C%20public%2C%20sexual%20assaults%20on%20the%20bodies%20of%20women%20%E2%80%98captured%E2%80%99%20with%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-police-women-video-paraded-naked%5C%22%3Epolice%20watching%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20shocked%20India%E2%80%99s%20moral%20conscience%20%E2%80%93%20and%20are%20being%20anything%20but%20contrite.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20has%20come%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwrestlers-protest-polirics-do-the-right-thing%5C%22%3Efeudal%20disregard%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20regime%20of%20the%20months-long%20sit-in%20protest%20by%20some%20of%20our%20internationally-acclaimed%20women%20wrestlers%20against%20sexual%20oppression%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20a%20BJP%20MP.%20The%20overall%20question%20of%20male%20lawlessness%20in%20the%20context%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20dignity%20and%20physical%20safety%20has%20angered%20public%20sentiment%20around%20the%20country.%20And%2C%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20parliamentary%20constituency%20of%20Varanasi%2C%20a%2060-year-old%20complex%20associated%20with%20Gandhian%20studies%20and%20social%20activities%20is%20being%20strong-armed%20by%20government%20and%20is%20threatened%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fsarva-seva-sangh-gandhian-society-varanasi-protests-illegal-demolition-notice-priyanka-gandhi-8693922%2F%5C%22%3Edemolition%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20leading%20to%20massive%20everyday%20protests.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThrough%20all%20this%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20remained%20unmoved.%20His%20silence%20and%20unseeing%20and%20uncaring%20attitude%20has%20dented%20his%20reputation.%20This%20worries%20many%20in%20his%20own%20party%20but%20they%20dare%20not%20complain%2C%20fearing%20the%20dungeon%20treatment.%20Nevertheless%2C%20there%20is%20thriving%20dissidence%20within%20BJP%20in%20key%20states.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19162700%2FWhatsApp-Image-2022-02-22-at-11.12.03.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19162700%2FWhatsApp-Image-2022-02-22-at-11.12.03.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19162700%2FWhatsApp-Image-2022-02-22-at-11.12.03-300x163.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F19162700%2FWhatsA