20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20Railways%20to%20%E2%80%9Cunnecessarily%20drag%E2%80%9D%20citizens%20into%20litigation.%20The%20court%20ordered%20the%20Railways%20to%20pay%20Rs%208.2%20lakh%20compensation%20to%20the%20petitioner%20(victim).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victim%20suffered%20the%20injury%20in%202012%20when%20he%20was%20on%20his%20way%20to%20the%20reservation%20counter%20at%20Thampanoor%20Railway%20Station%20in%20Thiruvananthapuram.%20A%20bullet%20pierced%20through%20his%20abdomen%20when%20a%20railway%20cop%20at%20the%20station%20misfired%20his%20gun.%20After%20examining%20his%20case%2C%20the%20railways%E2%80%99%20special%20board%20offered%20him%20Rs%201.20%20lakh%20as%20compensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20then%20approached%20the%20high%20court%20arguing%20that%20the%20amount%20paid%20in%20compensation%20is%20not%20enough%20for%20the%20level%20of%20trauma%20he%20had%20undergone.%20He%20also%20noted%20in%20his%20petition%20that%20the%20injury%20left%20him%20with%20a%20permanent%20disability%20and%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20lead%20a%20normal%20life.%20He%20sought%20Rs%2020%20lakh%20as%20compensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20railways%20challenged%20his%20petition%20and%20questioned%20the%20maintainability%20of%20his%20petition%2C%20underlining%20that%20a%20compensation%20of%20Rs%201.20%20lakh%20was%20already%20paid%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20examining%20the%20medical%20records%20of%20the%20petitioner%20and%20considering%20his%20agony%2C%20the%20court%20ordered%20Railways%20to%20pay%20the%20victim%20Rs%208.20%20lakh%20while%20pulling%20up%20the%20Railways.%20It%20said%20the%20petitioner%20is%20entitled%20to%20interest%20also%20for%20the%20said%20amount%20at%20the%20rate%20of%209%25%20per%20annum%20from%20the%20date%20of%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20of%20the%20considered%20opinion%20that%20in%20a%20situation%20like%20this%2C%20the%20Railway%20ought%20to%20have%20risen%20to%20the%20occasion%20and%20redress%20the%20grievance%20of%20the%20petitioner%20without%20asking%20the%20victim%2C%20like%20the%20petitioner%2C%20to%20lead%20a%20legal%20battle.%20All%20legal%20battles%20are%20worth%20fighting%2C%20but%20some%20are%20not%20worth%20winning%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20judge%20said%20in%20a%20word%20of%20advice%20to%20the%20Railways.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690013449000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F20105824%2F26554621.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ffocus-on-speedy-redressal-of-grievances-not-just-on-trains-like-vande-bharat-kerala-hc-to-railways%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20court%20slammed%20the%20railways%20over%20the%20delay%20in%20paying%20adequate%20compensation%20to%20a%20person%20who%20sustained%20a%20bullet%20injury%20in%202012%20after%20a%20railway%20policeman%20misfired.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ffocus-on-speedy-redressal-of-grievances-not-just-on-trains-like-vande-bharat-kerala-hc-to-railways%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Paytm%20to%20generate%20free%20cash%20flow%20by%20year%20end%2C%20says%20CEO%20Vijay%20Shekhar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690013105000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Fmisc%2F2022-12%2F12%2Ffull%2F20220922127L.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fpaytm-to-generate-free-cash-flow-by-year-end-says-ceo-vijay-shekhar-123072200243_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Its%20revenue%20from%20operations%20increased%20by%2039.4%20per%20cent%20to%20Rs%202%2C341.6%20crore%20during%20the%20reported%20quarter%20from%20Rs%201%2C679.6%20crore%20in%20the%20June%202022%20quarter%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnew