0Centre%20after%20this%20development%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20shot%20on%20May%204%20surfaced%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20showing%20two%20women%20from%20one%20of%20the%20warring%20communities%20in%20Manipur%20being%20paraded%20naked%20and%20molested%20by%20a%20mob%20from%20the%20other%20side.%20The%20alleged%20main%20accused%20was%20arrested%20on%20Thursday.%20The%20incident%20has%20drawn%20widespread%20condemnation%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20militants'%20statement%20said%20there%20is%20anger%20among%20Mizo%20youths%2C%20who%20are%20deeply%20anguished%20over%20the%20%26quot%3Bbarbaric%20and%20atrocious%20act%20of%20Meiteis%26quot%3B%20against%20Zo%20or%20Kuki%20ethnic%20people%20in%20Manipur%2C%20who%20share%20ancestry%20with%20the%20Mizos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20the%20appeal%20was%20only%20for%20Meiteis%20from%20Manipur%20and%20not%20those%20from%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20Meiteis%2C%20including%20students%2C%20mostly%20from%20Manipur%20and%20Assam%2C%20live%20in%20Mizoram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2012%2C000%20Kukis%20displaced%20from%20Manipur%20have%20also%20reportedly%20taken%20shelter%20in%20the%20northeastern%20state%2C%20which%20is%20Christian-dominated.%20Kukis%20are%20also%20mostly%20Christians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPAMRA%20is%20a%20non-political%20organisation%20of%20former%20Mizo%20National%20Front%20(MNF)%20militants%20seeking%20implementation%20of%20all%20clauses%20of%20the%20Mizo%20Peace%20Accord.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20160%20people%20have%20lost%20their%20lives%20and%20several%20injured%20since%20ethnic%20violence%20broke%20out%20in%20the%20state%20on%20May%203%2C%20when%20a%20'Tribal%20Solidarity%20March'%20was%20organised%20in%20the%20hill%20districts%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20Meitei%20community's%20demand%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20(ST)%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeiteis%20account%20for%20about%2053%20per%20cent%20of%20Manipur's%20populati