22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Oppenheimer%20Brings%20Cinema%20Back%20To%20Life%20In%20Kashmir%2C%20House%20Full%20On%20Day%201%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHollywood%20blockbuster%20%3Cem%3EOppenheimer%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20witnessing%20a%20phenomenal%20response%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20with%20capital%20Srinagar's%20lone%20multiplex%20reporting%20record%20sales%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20day%20the%20Christopher%20Nolan%20biopic%20was%20released.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESrinagar's%20only%20multiplex%20is%20sold%20out%20for%20the%20next%20three%20days%2C%20making%20%3Cem%3EOppenheimer%3C%2Fem%3E%20the%20biggest%20release%20in%20Kashmir%20after%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan's%20Pathaan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20a%20Hollywood%20epic%20thriller%20has%20achieved%20full%20house%20in%20Kashmir's%20only%20multiplex%20where%20Cinemas%20remained%20shut%20for%2033%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20the%20film%20was%20released%20tickets%20at%20Srinagar's%20INOX%20-%20the%20only%20multiplex%20in%20Kashmir-%20its%20tickets%20got%20sold%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVikas%20Dhar%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20INOX%2C%20said%20that%20the%20overwhelming%20response%20of%20people%20has%20surprised%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTickers%20are%20sold%20out%20for%20another%20few%20days.%20It%20has%20surpassed%20our%20expectations.%20We%20had%20never%20thought%20that%20a%20Hollywood%20film%20will%20get%20such%20a%20response%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Dhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EINOX%20in%20Srinagar%20was%20opened%20in%20September%20last%20year%20ending%20an%20entertainment%20draught%20in%20the%20Valley%20that%20was%20enforced%20following%20rise%20in%20terrorism%20in%201989.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Dhar%20says%20that%20the%20release%20of%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan's%20Pathaan%20was%20the%20turning%20point%20that%20attracted%20people%20to%20cinema%20in%20Kashmir%20and%20now%20its%20%3Cem%3EOppenheimer%3C%2Fem%3E%20which%20has%20achieved%20house%20full.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKashmirs%20cinema%20legacy%20is%20as%20old%20as%20Bollywood%20in%20India.%20The%20first%20cinema%20%26quot%3BKashmir%20Talkie%26quot%3B%20opened%20in%20Srinagar%20in%201932%2C%20two%20year%20before%20Bombay%20Talkies%20movie%20studio%20was%20founded%20in%20Mumbai.%20It%20was%20later%20named%20as%20Pladium%20cinema.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventuality%2C%20Regal%20cinema%20and%20several%20other%20movie%20theaters%20came%20up%20in%20Kashmir.%20Many%20of%20them%20were%20showing%20Hollywood%20films%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20the%20rise%20of%20terrorism%20backed%20by%20religious%20extremism%2C%20all%20cinemas%20were%20shut%20in%201989.%20Several%20attempts%20to%20reopen%20Cinema%20failed%20due%20to%20fear%20and%20lack%20of%20moviegoers%20in%20the%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EOppenheimer%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20film%20on%20the%20life%20of%20American%20physicist%20Robert%20Oppenheimer%20(called%20the%20%26quot%3Bfather%20of%20atomic%20bomb%26quot%3B)%20who%20developed%20the%20first%20atomic%20bombs%20that%20were%20later%20dropped%20on%20Hiroshima%20and%20Nagasaki%20in%201945%2C%20during%20the%20Second%20World%20War.%20The%20lead%20role%20in%20the%20R-rated%20film%20is%20played%20by%20Cillian%20Murphy%2C%20the%20star%20of%20'Peaky%20Blinders'.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690005000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fuopqv568_cinema-lovers-in-kashmir-_625x300_22_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchristopher-nolans-oppenheimer-brings-cinema-back-to-life-in-kashmir-house-full-on-day-1-4231274%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hollywood%20blockbuster%20Oppenheimer%20is%20witnessing%20a%20phenomenal%20response%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20with%20capital%20Srinagar's%20lone%20multiplex%20reporting%20record%20sales%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20day%20the%20Christopher%20Nolan%20biopic%20was%20released.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news