20accustomed%20to%20the%20new%20position.%20He%20has%20not%20scored%20big%20in%20the%20spot%20do%20far.%20While%20in%20the%20first%20Test%20in%20Dominica%20he%20scored%20six%2C%20in%20the%20first%20innings%20of%20the%20second%20Test%20in%20Trinidad%20he%20scored%2010.%20Former%20India%20opener%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Wasim%20Jaffer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F241-wasim-jaffer-playerprofile%5C%22%3EWasim%20Jaffer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20played%2031%20Tests%20and%20two%20ODIs%20for%20India%20and%20also%20holds%20numerous%20records%20in%20domestic%20cricket%2C%20said%20Gill%20will%20have%20to%20learn%20the%20trade%20of%20batting%20at%20No%203%2C%20especially%20on%20slow%20and%20low%20pitches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLooking%20at%20the%20bigger%20picture%2C%20he%20wants%20to%20bat%20there%20for%20a%20longer%20period.%20But%20the%20start%20has%20not%20been%20the%20way%20he%20wanted.%20In%20this%20Test%20match%20and%20in%20this%20innings%2C%20he%20had%20a%20good%20chance%2C%20the%20wicket%20was%20good%2C%20(the%20team)%20had%20got%20a%20good%20start.%20I%20felt%20he%20played%20a%20little%20loose%20and%20he%20obviously%20will%20be%20disappointed%20with%20that%20dismissal%2C%20and%20that%20is%20where%20he%20needs%20to%20tighten%20up.%20He%20likes%20the%20ball%20coming%20on%20to%20the%20bat%2C%20because%20of%20so%20much%20of%20white-ball%20cricket%20he%20is%20used%20to%20hitting%20on%20the%20rise%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20wants%20that%20pace%20which%20is%20found%20in%20white-ball%20cricket.%20But%20in%20red-ball%20cricket%2C%20on%20wickets%20like%20these%2C%20probably%20in%20India%20when%20he%20plays%2C%20it%20is%20not%20easy%20to%20play%20on%20the%20rise.%20He%20just%20needs%20to%20understand%20that%20and%20improve%20his%20game%20for%20those%20conditions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaffer%20said%20Jaiswal%20has%20made%20a%20great%20start%20to%20Test%20cricket%20which%20many%20players%20will