lm%20'The%20Canterbury%20Tales'%20and%20Richard%20Balducci's%20'L'odeur%20des%20fauves.'%20The%20same%20year%2C%20she%20also%20starred%20alongside%20Laurence%20Harvey%20in%20Menahem%20Golan's%201972%20drama%20'Escape%20to%20the%20Sun'%20about%20a%20group%20of%20people%20attempting%20to%20flee%20the%20Soviet%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20in%201984%2C%20she%20starred%20in%20the%20Canadian%20drama%20%3Ci%3EThe%20Bay%20Boy%3C%2Fi%3E%2C%20a%20film%20that%20marked%20the%20start%20of%20her%20co-star%20Kiefer%20Sutherland's%20acting%20career.%20In%201988%2C%20she%20starred%20as%20Hadley%20Richardson%2C%20opposite%20Stacy%20Keach%20as%20Ernest%20Hemingway%2C%20in%20the%20television%20mini-series%20'Hemingway%2C'%20as%20per%20Variety.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689998580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fuqroc4eo_josephine_625x300_22_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fcharlie-chaplin-s-daughter-josephine-chaplin-passes-away-at-74-4231095%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Josephine%20Chaplin%20began%20her%20career%20on%20screen%20at%20a%20young%20age%20in%20her%20father's%201952%20film%20Limelight%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fcharlie-chaplin-s-daughter-josephine-chaplin-passes-away-at-74-4231095%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fcharlie-chaplin-s-daughter-josephine-chaplin-passes-away-at-74-4231095%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fcharlie-chaplin-s-daughter-josephine-chaplin-passes-away-at-74-4231095%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli%20Reminds%20West%20Indies%20Legend%20Of%20Javed%2