0head%20coach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20us%20as%20a%20team%2C%20it%20is%20not%20important%20what%20is%20happening%20around%20us.%20How%20we%20play%20our%20brand%20of%20cricket%20is%20more%20important.%20We%20will%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20the%20series%20to%20finish%20and%20see%20what%20happens%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20swashbuckling%20batter%20has%20been%20struggling%20for%20runs%20in%20the%20ongoing%20tour%20of%20Bangladesh.%20Mandhana%20managed%20a%20total%20of%2052%20runs%20in%20the%20three-match%20T20I%20series%20while%20she%20made%2011%20and%2036%20in%20the%20first%20and%20second%20ODIs%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20batting%20well%20in%20the%20nets%20and%20in%20the%20matches%20I%20have%20been%20getting%20starts.%20It%20doesn't%20happen%20very%20often%20that%20I%20am%20middling%20the%20ball%20and%20still%20not%20getting%20runs%20for%20the%20team%20but%20I%20have%20been%20working%20on%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20last%20match%20for%20me%20was%20pretty%20positive%2C%20the%20way%20I%20was%20able%20to%20get%20the%20team%20off%20to%20a%20decent%20start%20but%20threw%20my%20wicket%20away.%20It's%20more%20about%20application..%20my%20batting%20is%20going%20well%20but%20application%20hasn't%20been%20always%20the%20way%20I%20applied%2C%26quot%3B%20Mandhana%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20team%20succumbed%20to%20its%20first-ever%20WODI%20loss%20to%20Bangladesh%20in%20the%20series%20opener%20and%20Mandhana%20said%20the%20hosts%20have%20evolved%20as%20a%20side%20in%20the%20past%20one%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20played%20them%20in%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20last%20year%2C%20they%20have%20grown%20since%20then.%20On%20these%20sort%20of%20wickets%20their%20bowling%20attack%20is%20good.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20played%20a%20very%20good%20brand%20of%20cricket.%20They%20will%20be%20coming%20hard%20at%20us%20so%20we%20won't%20be%20taking%20anything%20lightly.