Farticleshow%2F102029578.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2029-year-old%20pace%20bowler%20Mukesh%20Kumar%20became%20the%20308th%20Test%20cricketer%20to%20represent%20India.%20The%20prestigious%20debut%20cap%20was%20presented%20to%20him%20by%20premier%20spinner%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20ahead%20of%20the%202nd%20Test%20match%20between%20India%20and%20West%20Indies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A17%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Findia-in-west-indies%2Fwatch-pacer-mukesh-kumars-emotional-phone-call-with-his-mother-after-test-debut%2Farticleshow%2F102029578.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%2010-Year-Old%20Girl%20Has%20Visited%2050%20Countries%20Without%20Missing%20A%20School%20Day%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2010-year-old%20girl%2C%20Aditi%20Tripathi%2C%20has%20already%20visited%2050%20countries%20with%20her%20globetrotting%20parents%2C%20that%20too%20without%20missing%20a%20single%20day%20of%20school.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3EYahoo%20Life%20UK%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Aditi%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20South%20London%20with%20her%20father%20Deepak%20and%20mother%20Avilasha%2C%20has%20travelled%20to%20most%20of%20Europe%20and%20has%20even%20been%20to%20places%20like%20Nepal%2C%20Singapore%20and%20Thailand.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fuk.style.yahoo.com%2Fstyle%2F50-countries-before-10th-birthday-120040743.html%5C%22%3Eoutlet%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Aditi's%20parents%20decided%20early%20on%20that%20they%20wanted%20their%20child%20to%20be%20a%20well-travelled%20individual.%20They%20wanted%20her%20to%20experience%20the%20world%20and%20understand%20different%20cultures%2C%20foods%20and%20people%2C%20without%20losing%20any%20progress%20at%20school.%20So%20they%20devised%20a%20plan%20and%20started%20travelling%20during%20every%20school%20holiday%20and%20even%20started%20utilising%20bank%20holidays.%20Aditi's%20parents%20estimate%20they%20spend%2020%2C000%20Pounds%20(over%20Rs%2021%20Lakhs)%20a%20year%20on%20travel%2C%20but%20they%20say%20it's%20worth%20every%20penny.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20gets%20curious%20and%20excited%20seeing%20different%20cultures%20like%20in%20Nepal%2C%20India%20and%20Thailand.%20We%20started%20travelling%20with%20her%20when%20she%20was%20in%20nursery%20age%20three%20and%20she%20used%20to%20go%20to%20school%20for%20two%20and%20a%20half%20days%20per%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Tripathi%2C%20as%20per%20Yahoo.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20we%20pick%20her%20up%20straight%20from%20school%20on%20Friday%20and%20we%20take%20late%20night%20flight%20back%20at%20around%2011pm%20on%20Sunday.%20Sometimes%20we%20have%20arrived%20on%20the%20Monday%20morning%2C%20and%20she%20goes%20straight%20to%20school%20from%20the%20airport%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fgame-that-has-lasted-over-500-virtual-years-breaks-football-manager-record-4230782%5C%22%3EGame%20That%20Has%20Lasted%20Over%20500%20Virtual%20Years%20Breaks%20'Football%20Manager'%20Record%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmetro.co.uk%2F2023%2F07%2F18%2Fi-spend-20k-taking-my-child-on-holiday-shes-seen-50-countries-19146754%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMetro%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Aditi's%20parents%20work%20as%20accountants%20and%20they%20save%20throughout%20the%20year%20for%20their%20trips.%20They%20avoid%20eating%20out%2C%20rely%20on%20public%20transport%2C%20do%20not%20own%20a%20car%20and%20also%20work%20from%20home%20in%20order%20to%20save%20on%20commuting%20costs%20and%20childcare%20for%20Aditi's%202-year-old%20sister%20Advita.%20Before%2C%20Covid%2C%20Mr%20Tripathi%20revealed%20that%20they%20would%20travel%20to%20around%2012%20places%20in%20a%20year.%20Aditi%20has%20visited%20almost%20every%20country%20in%20Europe%20despite%20her%20tender%20age%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Thailand%2C%20Indonesia%20and%20Singapore%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20have%20a%20specific%20favourite%20country%20or%20place%20but%20if%20I%20had%20to%20choose%20three%20it%20would%20be%20Nepal%2C%20Georgia%2C%20Armenia%2C%26quot%3B%20Aditi%20said%2C%20as%20per%20the%20outlet.%20%26quot%3BNepal%20was%20probably%20one%20of%20my%20favourites%20because%20I%20did%20horse%20riding%2C%20I%20went%20on%20the%20longest%20cable%20car%2C%20and%20I%20could%20see%20mountains%20like%20Mount%20Everest.%20I%20really%20love%20travelling%20and%20have%20loads%20of%20fun%20memories.%20I%20would%20recommend%20it%20to%20other%20children%20because%20it%20can%20really%20help%20with%20your%20social%20skills%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAditi's%20first%20trip%20was%20to%20Germany%20when%20she%20was%20aged%20just%20three.%20Inspired%20by%20their%20love%20of%20the%20first%20trip%2C%20they%20soon%20visited%20France%2C%20Italy%20and%20Austria%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689995820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fufmkogio_aditi-tripathi_625x300_22_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Findian-origin-girl-10-has-visited-50-countries-without-missing-school-day-her-story-is-now-viral-4231101%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%2010-year-old%20girl%2C%20Aditi%20Tripathi%2C%20has%20already%20visited%2050%20countries%20with%20her%20globetrotting%20parents%2C%20that%20too%20without%20missing%20a%20single%20day%20of%20school.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A39%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Findian-origin-girl-10-has-visited-50-countries-without-missing-school-day-her-story-is-now-viral-4231101%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Findian-origin-girl-10-has-visited-50-countries-w