0running%20on%20to%20the%20field%20before%20being%20apprehended%20by%20security.%20Smoke%20bombs%20in%20Miami's%20trademark%20pink%20went%20off%20in%20the%20area%20behind%20the%20goal%2C%20occupied%20by%20the%20team's%20most%20passionate%20supporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMiami%20and%20Major%20League%20Soccer%20hope%20that%20the%20arrival%20of%20the%20Argentine%20World%20Cup%20winner%20and%20all-time%20great%2C%20will%20transform%20the%20sport%20and%20push%20it%20into%20the%20American%20mainstream.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Messi's%20debut%20was%20any%20guide%2C%20the%20former%20Barcelona%20star%20still%20has%20plenty%20to%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20his%20wonderful%20goal%20he%20had%20looked%20sharp%20and%20alert%2C%20his%20touch%20belying%20the%20fact%20that%20until%20little%20over%20a%20week%20ago%20he%20was%20vacationing%20on%20a%20Caribbean%20beach%20with%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sergio%20Busquets%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Fplayers%2F94365-sergio-busquets-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESergio%20Busquets%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Spanish%20midfielder%20and%20former%20Barca%20team-mate%2C%20who%20has%20joined%20Messi%20for%20his%20American%20adventure%2C%20also%20made%20a%20strong%20impression%20after%20they%20both%20entered%20the%20contest%20in%20the%2054th%20minute%20as%20part%20of%20a%20triple%20change%20with%20Venezuelan%20Josef%20Martinez.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusquets%20showed%20his%20famous%2C%20almost%20telepathic%20understanding%20with%20Messi%20remains%2C%20after%20over%20two%20years%20apart%20from%20each%20other%2C%20with%20the%20midfielder%20delivering%20pieces%20from%20all%20angles%20into%20the%20Argentine's%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20was%20Messi's%20magical%20finish%20that%20will%20remain%20long%20in%20the%20memories%20of%20Inter%20Miami%20fans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20knew%20I%20had%20to%20score%2C%20it%20was%20the%20last%20play%20of%20the%20game.%20I%20wanted%20to%20score%20so%20we%20didn't%20go%20to%20penalties.%20It%20was%20very%20important%20for%20us%20to%20get%20this%20win%2C%20it's%20a%20new%20tournament%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20give%20us%20confidence%20moving%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Argentine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Leagues%20Cup%20group%20teams%20are%20awarded%20a%20point%20each%20for%20a%20draw%20and%20then%20the%20winner%20of%20a%20penalty%20shoot-out%20gets%20an%20additional%20point%2C%20but%20Messi%20made%20sure%20Miami%20grabbed%20all%20three%20for%20a%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20made%20sure%20that%20the%20club's%20co-owner%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22David%20Beckham%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Fplayers%2F105059-david-beckham-playerprofile%5C%22%3EDavid%20Beckham%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20a%20broad%20grin%20at%20the%20final%20whistle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20be%20honest%2C%20as%20soon%20as%20I%20saw%20the%20free%20kick%20given%20I%20thought%20this%20is%20the%20way%20it's%20meant%20to%20end.%20Especially%20when%20you've%20got%20players%20like%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Leo%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Fplayers%2F90758-leo-playerprofile%5C%22%3ELeo%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Sergio%20on%20the%20pitch%2C%20that's%20what%20they%20produce%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20former%20England%20midfielder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20so%20exciting%20tonight%20for%20our%20fans.%20All%20of%20these%20people%20that%20come%20down%20here%20to%20see%20Leo%20just%20step%20onto%20the%20pitch%2C%20let%20alone%20just%20do%20what%20he's%20done.%20It's%20a%20dream%20come%20true%20for%20everyone%20in%20this%20stadium%20to%20see.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20such%20a%20moment%20for%20this%20country%2C%20such%20a%20moment%20for%20this%20league%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EStars%20turn%20out%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMessi%20became%20the%20biggest%20name%20signing%20in%20MLS's%20history%20when%20h