%20connectivity%2C%20even%20as%20they%20greenlighted%20feasibility%20studies%20for%20a%20pipeline%20and%20land%20bridge%20between%20the%20two%20South%20Asian%20neighbours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fsri-lanka-visit-political-issues-on-back-burner-connectivity-economic-matters-on-the-front%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20first%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Thursday%20that%20connectivity%20was%20going%20to%20be%20the%20main%20theme%20of%20the%20first%20visit%20of%20Ranil%20Wickremesinghe%20to%20India%20after%20taking%20over%20as%20President%20a%20year%20ago.%20As%20expected%2C%20India%20urged%20for%20the%20longstanding%20position%20on%20implementing%20the%2013th%20amendment%20and%20called%20on%20Sri%20Lanka%20to%20respect%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Csensitivities%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Sri%20Lanka%20defaulting%20on%20its%20external%20debt%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20its%20history%2C%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20country%20has%20faced%20economic%20challenges%20as%20it%20was%20unable%20to%20buy%20most%20of%20its%20essential%20commodities%20due%20to%20its%20depleted%20foreign%20currency%20reserves.%20Last%20year%2C%20India%20had%20extended%20an%20emergency%20assistance%20of%20%244%20billion.%20The%20South%20Asian%20giant%20had%20also%20formed%20a%20group%20with%20Japan%20and%20other%20Paris%20Club%20members%20to%20negotiate%20the%20restructuring%20of%20Sri%20Lanka%E2%80%99s%20External%20debt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20arriving%20on%20Thursday%20evening%2C%20Wickremesinghe%20held%20a%20series%20of%20meetings%20with%20Indian%20External%20Affairs%20minister%20S.%20Jaishankar%2C%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Ajit%20Doval%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgautam_adani%2Fstatus%2F1682211101063393281%5C%22%3EAdani%20Group%20chairman%20Gautam%20Adani%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20called%20on%20President%20Draupadi%20Murmu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20afternoon%2C%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20visitor%20held%20formal%20talks%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20witnessed%20the%20signing%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmea.gov.in%2Fbilateral-documents.htm%3Fdtl%2F36867%2FList_of_Outcomes_Official_Visit_of_the_President_of_Sri_Lanka_to_India%5C%22%3Efive%20bilateral%20documents%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20roller%20coaster%20nature%20of%20India-Sri%20Lanka%20ties%20in%20recent%20years%20due%20to%20Colombo%E2%80%99s%20ties%20with%20China%2C%20Modi%20said%20that%20the%20security%20interests%20of%20both%20nations%20are%20%E2%80%9Cintertwined%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20therefore%2C%20it%20is%20essential%20that%20we%20work%20together%20keeping%20in%20mind%20each%20other%E2%80%99s%20safety%20and%20sensitivities%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmea.gov.in%2FSpeeches-Statements.htm%3Fdtl%2F36862%2FEnglish_translation_of_Press_Statement_by_Prime_Minister_Shri_Narendra_Modi_during_the_visit_of_the_President_of_Sri_Lanka_to_India%5C%22%3EIn%20his%20press%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Modi%20noted%20that%20they%20had%20adopted%20a%20vision%20document%20for%20economic%20partnership%2C%20titled%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmea.gov.in%2Fbilateral-documents.htm%3Fdtl%2F36864%2FPromoting_Connectivity_Catalysing_Prosperity_IndiaSri_Lanka_Economic_Partnership_Vision%5C%22%3EPromoting%20Connectivity%2C%20Catalysing%20Prosperity%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20vision%20is%20to%20strengthen%20Maritime%2C%20Air%2C%20Energy%2C%20and%20people-to-people%20connectivity%20between%20the%20people%20of%20both%20countries.%20This%20vision%20is%20to%20accelerate%20mutual%20cooperation%20in%20tourism%2C%20power%2C%20trade%2C%20higher%20education%2C%20and%20skill%20development.%20This%20vision%20is%20India%E2%80%99s%20long-term%20commitment%20to%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20there%20is%20a%20single%20flight%20a%20day%20between%20Chennai%20and%20the%20northern%20Lankan%20city%20of%20Jaffna.%20The%20two%20leaders%20agreed%20to%20expand%20this%20flight%20%E2%80%9Cto%20Colombo%20as%20well%20as%20explore%20connectivity%20between%20Chennai%20and%20Trincomalee%2C%20Batticaloa%20and%20other%20destinations%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20ferry%20services%20will%20be%20additional%20passenger%20Ferry%20Services%20between%20Nagapattinam%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Kankesanthurai%20in%20Sri%20Lanka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CApart%20from%20this%2C%20it%20was%20also%20decided%20to%20check%20the%20feasibility%20of%20a%20land%20bridge%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnnouncing%20another%20feasibility%20study%20for%20a%20gas%20pipeline%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmd.gov.lk%2Fnews%2Fstrengthening-historic-indo-lanka-joint-vision-for-the-next-25-years%2F%5C%22%3EWickremesinghe%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cconstruction%20of%20a%20multi-product%20petroleum%20pipeline%20from%20Southern%20part%20of%20India%20to%20Sri%20Lanka%20will%20ensure%20an%20affordable%20and%20reliable%20supply%20of%20energy%20resources%20to%20Sri%20Lanka%E2%80%9D.%20The%20work%20on%20connecting%20the%20electricity%20grids%20will%20also%20be%20expedited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20leaders%20also%20talked%20about%20developing%20the%20northern%20port%20of%20Trincomalee%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9Cenergy%20hub%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20ongoing%20cooperation%20in%20the%20development%20of%20Trincomalee%20Tank%20Farms%20is%20a%20reflection%20of%20our%20endeavour%20to%20develop%20mutually%20beneficial%20cooperation%20projects%20in%20Trincomalee%20area%2C%20and%20agreed%20to%20further%20develop%20Trincomalee%20as%20a%20national%20and%20regional%20hub%20of%20industry%2C%20energy%20and%20economic%20activity%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20mutual%20understanding%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20%E2%80%98Vision%E2%80%99%20document.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20extolling%20the%20need%20for%20enhanced%20connectivity%2C%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20President%20noted%20that%20it%20would%20increase%20people-to-people%20exchanges%20and%20cultural%20ties.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20tourism%20industry%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%20is%20poised%20to%20reap%20the%20benefits%20of%20the%20post-pandemic%20world%20and%20India%20is%20currently%20the%20top%20market%20for%20inbound%20tourism%20for%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20that%20context%2C%20Wickremesinghe%20said%20that%20enabling%20India%E2%80%99s%20UPI-based%20digital%20payment%20would%20facilitate%20the%20growth%20in%20Indian%20tourist%20and%20economic%20activity%20in%20Sri%20Lanka.%20An%20agreement%20between%20NIPL%20and%20Lanka%20Pay%20was%20inked%20for%20UPI%20application%20acceptance%20in%20Sri%20Lanka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%20also%20announced%20that%20the%20stalled%20talks%20for%20negotiating%20the%20Economic%20and%20Technological%20Cooperation%20Agreement%20(ETCA)%20will%20be%20%E2%80%9Cstarted%20soon%E2%80%9D.%20Sri%20Lanka%20already%20has%20a%20FTA%20with%20India%2C%20but%20New%20Delhi%20had%20been%20seeking%20a%20more%20expanded%20version%20which%20will%20not%20be%20as%20stacked%20to%20Colombo%E2%80%99s%20advantage.%20Talks%20for%20an%20ETCA%20had%20taken%20place%20for%20several%20years%20during%20the%20Maithripala%20Sirisena%20presidency%20but%20were%20suspended%20in%202018%20with%20no%20headway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20mark%20200%20years%20of%20the%20arrival%20of%20Indians%20to%20work%20in%20tea%20plantations%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Modi%20announced%20a%20package%20of%20Rs%2075%20crore%20for%20development%20projects%20targeting%20Indian-origin%20Tamil%20citizens%20of%20Sri%20Lanka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWickremesinghe%20said%20that%20he%20shared%20the%20comprehensive%20proposal%20for%20%E2%80%9Creconciliation%2C%20power%20sharing%20through%20devolution%20and%20the%20multiple%20elements%20of%20the%20Northern%20development%20plan%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20invited%20all%20party%20leaders%20in%20Parliament%20to%20work%20towards%20consensus%20and%20national%20unity%20on%20these%20measures.%20Thereafter%20the%20Government%20will%20place%20the%20relevant%20legislation%20before%20Parliament%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20stated%20in%20his%20press%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20long-pending%20issue%20of%20the%20devolution%20of%20powers%2C%20Modi%20hoped%20that%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20government%20will%20fulfill%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20aspiration%20of%20the%20Tamils%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20well%20as%2C%20%E2%80%9Cits%20commitment%20to%20implement%20the%20Thirteenth%20Amendment%20and%20conduct%20the%20Provincial%20Council%20Elections%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20PM%20asserted%20that%20this%20will%20ensure%20that%20the%20Tamil%20community%20of%20Sri%20Lanka%20has%20a%20%E2%80%9Clife%20of%20respect%20and%20dignity%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2013th%20constitutional%20amendment%20was%20a%20result%20of%20the%201987%20Indo-Lanka%20accord%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20the%20creation%20of%20provinces.%20However%2C%20the%20accord%20has%20to%20be%20fully%20implemented%20as%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20government%20has%20balked%20at%20devolving%20police%20and%20revenue%20powers%20to%20the%20provinces%20as%20envisaged%20in%20the%20agreement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWickremesinghe%20stated%20that%20he%20shared%20his%20recently-unveiled%20%E2%80%9Ccomprehensive%20proposal%E2%80%9D%20for%20power-sharing%20and%20reconciliation.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20invited%20all%20party%20leaders%20in%20Parliament%20to%20work%20towards%20consensus%20and%20national%20unity%20on%20these%20measures.%20Thereafter%20the%20Government%20will%20place%20the%20relevant%20legislation%20before%20Parliament%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20his%20India%20visit%2C%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20leader%20had%20met%20with%20a%20group%20of%20Sri%20Lankan%20Tamil%20lawmakers%2C%20but%20both%20sides%20had%20not%20been%20able%20to%20find%20any%20common%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689961525000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21231128%2FUntitled-design-2023-07-21T230526.275.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-sri-lanka-focus-on-connectivity-linkages-agree-on-studies-for-gas-pipeline-land-bridge%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%20also%20announced%20that%20the%20stalled%20talks%20for%20negotiating%20the%20Economic%20and%20Technological%20Cooperation%20Agreement%20(ETCA)%20will%20be%20'started%20soon'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-sri-lanka-focus-on-connectivity-linkages-agree-on-studies-for-gas-pipeline-land-bridge%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%3A%20Did%20Mass%20Arms%20Loot%20Strengthen%20the%20Mob%20to%20Sexually%20Assault%20Women%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F04085450%2FFvO7YL1aEAAlR43.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20FIR%20lodged%20in%20the%20case%20of%20rape%20of%20two%20Kuki%20women%20which%20happened%20on%20May%204%20puts%20the%20onus%20on%20the%20police%20for%20not%20doing%20enough%20to%20prevent%20the%20horrendous%20tragedy.%20%E2%80%9CHowever%20they%20%5Bthe%20rape%20survivors%20and%20two%20of%20their%20family%20members%5D%20were%20blocked%20on%20the%20way%20%5Bwhen%20they%20were%20trying%20to%20flee%20because%20of%20the%20attack%5D%20by%20a%20mob%20and%20snatched%20them%20from%20the%20custody%20of%20police%20team%20by%20the%20violent%20mob%20near%20Toubul.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20FIR%2C%20which%20was%20lodged%20on%20May%2018%20at%20Kangpokpi%20police%20station%2C%20was%20later%20transferred%20to%20Yairipok%20police%20station%20under%20Thoubal%20district.%20The%20rape%20was%20committed%20at%20B.Phainom%20village%20which%20comes%20under%20the%20Yairipok%20police%20station.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDid%20the%20%3Cspan%3Emass%20loot%20of%20police%20armoury%20by%20the%20violent%20mobs%20across%20the%20state%2C%20beginning%20on%20May%204%2C%20strengthen%20the%20resolve%20of%20this%20particular%20mob%20which%20raped%20and%20paraded%20the%20two%20Kuki%20women%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20may%20be%20mentioned%20here%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1RmiYxsuZk25pBG56JNiNcMWWO8_S1x-G9i9tqq6eBwc%2Fedit%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20had%20reported%20earlier%20how%20weapons%20of%20all%20types%20had%20been%20stolen%20by%20groups%20of%20people%20from%20various%20police%20stations%20and%20the%20police%20personnel%20deployed%20there%20hardly%20could%20offer%20any%20resistance.%20Various%20FIRs%20lodged%20earlier%20into%20the%20loot%20of%20police%20weapons%20say%20the%20mobs%20looted%20weapons%20even%20like%20Insas%20rifles%2C%20SLR%20rifles%2C%20AK%20assault%20rifles%20to%20pistols%2C%20magazines%20and%20whatever%20weaponry%20they%20found.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20complainant%20%E2%80%93%20the%20village%20chief%20of%20B.%20Phainom%20village%20%E2%80%93%20who%20lodged%20an%20FIR%20in%20the%20case%20of%20gang%20rape%20claimed%20that%20police%20stood%20almost%20as%20bystanders.%20The%20accounts%20of%20survivors%20narrated%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-police-women-video-paraded-naked%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20also%20say%20the%20same.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20Thoubal%20SP%2C%20Sachidananda%2C%20while%20talking%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fmanipur-video-rape-fir-gathered-dust-for-62-days-as-high-level-meetings-went-on-8851344%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20said%20the%20claim%20was%20false.%20%E2%80%9CThat%20very%20day%2C%20the%20Nongpok%20Sekmai%20police%20station%20was%20being%20mobbed%20by%20people%20trying%20to%20loot%20arms.%20Police%20were%20busy%20guarding%20the%20police%20station%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20newspaper%20quoted%20him%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20can%20an%20SP%20hide%20behind%20the%20fact%20a%20PS%20under%20his%20jurisdiction%20was%20mobbed%20and%20hence%20his%20men%20could%20not%20respond%20to%20an%20SOS%20situation%2C%E2%80%9D%20asks%20S.R.%20Dararpuri%2C%20a%20retired%20IPS%20officer.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20was%20the%20police%20station%20mobbed%3F%20Exactly%20at%20the%20same%20time%20when%20this%20gruesome%20incident%20was%20happening%2C%20Darapuri%20wondered.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20made%20multiple%20calls%20to%20Thoubal%20SP%20and%20sent%20him%20an%20SMS%20to%20seek%20his%20clarification.%20He%20responded%20to%20none.%20It%20is%20also%20not%20known%20if%20an%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20into%20the%20mobbing%20of%20the%20police%20station%2C%20if%20what%20SP%20is%20claiming%20is%20true.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDarapuri%20said%20looting%20of%20police%20weapons%20is%20a%20rare%20incident.%20But%20if%20one%20goes%20by%20the%20FIRs%2C%20which%20had%20been%20lodged%20in%20various%20police%20stations%20across%20the%20state%20giving%20details%20of%20such%20loots%2C%20it%20seemed%20something%20very%20common%20to%20be%20happening%20in%20Manipur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20never%20heard%20such%20large-scale%20mobbing%20of%20police%20stations%20in%20my%20entire%20career%20of%2032%20years.%20Rarely%20what%20would%20happen%20is%20a%20patrol%20party%20is%20mobbed%2C%20and%20the%20weapons%20looted%20or%20a%20small%20outpost%20looted%2C%E2%80%9D%20Darapuri%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20incidents%20of%20mass%20arms%20loot%20must%20have%20wiped%20out%20the%20fear%20of%20the%20state%20and%20its%20police.%20And%20therefore%2C%20any%20violent%20mob%20would%20not%20think%20twice%20before%20doing%20anything%20gruesome%2C%20including%20rapes%20and%20parading%20women%20naked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20official%20number%20cited%20but%20according%20to%20various%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2F140-weapons-surrendered-manipur-amit-shah-8642463%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eestimates%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E3%2C000%20weapons%20had%20been%20looted%20till%20last%20month.%20State%E2%80%99s%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20and%20even%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%20have%20made%20repeated%20appeals%20to%20people%20to%20return%20the%20arms.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAny%20loot%20of%20police%20weapons%20is%20followed-up%20by%20raids%20and%20arrests.%20Had%20the%20Manipur%20government%20and%20its%20police%20done%20any%20of%20this%20in%20the%20initial%20phase%2C%20not%20only%20the%20subsequent%20loot%20incidents%20would%20have%20stopped%20but%20even%20the%20arms%20would%20have%20been%20surrendered%2C%E2%80%9D%20Darapuri%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20the%20State%20had%20done%20so%2C%20it%20raises%20questions%20if%20it%20was%20complicit%20in%20the%20unprecedented%20stealth%20of%20police%20armoury%2C%20the%20former%20IPS%20officer%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20for%20the%20survivors%20of%20the%20May%204%20incident%2C%20they%20should%20have%20been%20provided%20with%20immediate%20police%20protection.%20Moreover%2C%20even%20if%20the%20police%20were%20not%20able%20to%20protect%20the%20survivors%20because%20of%20whatever%20reason%2C%20they%20should%20have%20lodged%20an%20FIR%20about%20the%20incident%20immediately.%20Neither%20of%20these%20two%20things%20happened.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20learnt%20that%20the%20survivors%20were%20not%20provided%20any%20protection%20because%20police%20did%20not%20swing%20into%20action%20at%20all%20till%20the%20video%20became%20viral.%20As%20far%20as%20the%20immediate%20lodging%20of%20the%20FIR%20is%20concerned%2C%20that%20also%20did%20not%20happen.%20After%2011%20days%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20village%20where%20these%20women%20and%20their%20family%20members%20lived%20lodged%20an%20FIR.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689959926000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F04085450%2FFvO7YL1aEAAlR43.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-did-mass-arms-loot-strengthen-the-mob-to-sexually-assault-women%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Any%20violent%20mob%20would%20not%20think%20twice%20before%20doing%20anything%20gruesome%2C%20including%20rapes%20and%20parading%20women%20naked%2C%20knowing%20that%20police%20are%20left%20with%20no%20weaponry%2C%20said%20a%20retired%20police%20officer.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-did-mass-arms-loot-strengthen-the-mob-to-sexually-assault-women%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Paytm%20Q1%20results%3A%20Loss%20narrows%20to%20Rs%20358.4%20crore%2C%20revenue%20jumps%2039.4%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689959048000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-03%2F27%2Ffull%2F1679938864-8772.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fpaytm-loss-narrows-to-rs-358-4-cr-revenue-jumps-39-4-in-jun