ll-corners%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eheavy%20criticism%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20from%20several%20quarters%20including%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2F400-ecologists-write-to-environment-minister-against-amendments-to-forest-conservation-act%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Escientists%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20conservationists%2C%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fcitizens-climate-action-groups-protest-against-the-passage-of-forest-conservation-amendment-bill%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520protests%2520happened%2520in%2520Delhi%2Cto%2520political%2520leaders%2520and%2520MPs.%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eactivists%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20One%20of%20the%20many%20reasons%20is%20that%20its%20implementation%20will%20open%20large%20tracts%20of%20forest%20land%20to%20different%20kinds%20of%20land%20use%20changes%20%E2%80%94%20including%20developmental%20activities%20such%20as%20tourism%20%E2%80%94%20without%20the%20need%20for%20forest%20clearances.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConservationists%20have%20said%20that%20the%20report%20will%20%E2%80%9Cunleash%20devastation%E2%80%9D%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20forests%20and%20wildlife.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20Bill%20and%20the%20JPC%E2%80%99s%20report%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Forest%20(Conservation)%20Amendment%20Bill%202023%2C%20which%20was%20tabled%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%20March%2C%20was%20referred%20to%20a%20Joint%20Parliamentary%20Committee.%20This%20goes%20against%20standard%20procedure%3A%20bills%20pertaining%20to%20the%20environment%20are%20usually%20referred%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Fparliamentary-committees%2Fscience-technology-environment-forests%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EStanding%20Parliamentary%20Committee%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20currently%20headed%20by%20former%20environment%20minister%20and%20Congress%20leader%20Jairam%20Ramesh.%20Ramesh%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fjairam-ramesh-protests-as-bill-to-amend-forest-act-not-sent-to-parliamentary-standing-committee%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eobjected%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20the%20move%20to%20refer%20the%20FCA%20Amendment%20Bill%20to%20a%20JPC.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Committee%20received%201%2C309%20memoranda%2C%20which%20were%20circulated%20to%20all%20its%20members%20(who%20presented%20four%20dissent%20notes)%2C%20and%20also%20sent%20to%20the%20Union%20environment%20ministry%20for%20comments.%20The%20Committee%20also%20consulted%2012%20experts%20who%20presented%20their%20views%20in%20front%20of%20the%20Committee.%20The%20Committee%20also%20called%20for%20suggestions%20from%20other%20ministries%20including%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%2C%20it%20said%20in%20its%20report.%20It%20considered%20the%20bill%20clause-by-clause.%20The%20JPC%20tabled%20the%20200-odd%20page%20Report%20in%20Parliament%20on%20July%2020%2C%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20Monsoon%20Session.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Report%20clears%20all%20the%20changes%20suggested%20by%20the%20Union%20environment%20ministry%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Forest%20(Conservation)%20Amendment%20Bill%202023.%20These%20include%20issues%20that%20experts%20have%20pointed%20out%2C%20right%20from%20the%20new%20Preamble%20that%20the%20Bill%20proposes%20to%20introduce%20in%20the%20Act%2C%20to%20how%20it%20glosses%20over%20specifications%20such%20as%20the%20way%20it%20aims%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fforest-governance-india-people%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EGodavarman%20judgment%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%201996%20will%20not%20be%20overridden.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Godavarman%20judgment%20is%20crucial%20as%20it%20detailed%20that%20a%20%E2%80%98forest%E2%80%99%20must%20be%20defined%20according%20to%20its%20dictionary%20meaning%2C%20irrespective%20of%20the%20nature%20of%20its%20ownership%20and%20classification.%20This%20was%20woven%20into%20the%20FCA%20and%20states%20could%20no%20longer%20de-reserve%20protected%20forests%20for%20non-forestry%20use%20(commercial%20or%20industrial)%20without%20permission.%20But%20that%20will%20change%20with%20the%20amendment%20to%20this%20clause%20that%20the%20Bill%20proposes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98Lets%20India%E2%80%99s%20citizens%20down%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20JPC%20report%20lets%20down%20the%20citizens%20of%20the%20country%20for%20several%20reasons%20including%20the%20fact%20that%20most%20comments%20raised%20by%20experts%20and%20citizens%20have%20not%20been%20addressed%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fprernabindra%2Fstatus%2F1682319980451311616%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20conservationist%20and%20journalist%20Prerna%20Singh%20Bindra%2C%20in%20a%20joint%20statement%20with%20conservationist%20Prakriti%20Srivastava.%20Bindra%20said%20that%20the%20report%20%E2%80%9Cignores%20critique%2C%20genuine%20concerns%20of%20citizens%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20%E2%80%9Cunleashes%20devastation%E2%80%9D%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20forests%20and%20wildlife.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20JPC%20Report%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FForest%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Forest%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FConservation%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Conservation%3C%2Fa%3E%20Bill%202023%20ignores%20critque%2Cgenuine%20concerns%20of%20citzens%2Cpasses%20the%20bill%20as%20is%2Cunleashing%20devastation%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F