clarify%20whether%20the%20commissioner%20of%20railway%20safety%20(CRS)%20had%20submitted%20its%20report%20regarding%20the%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20rear-collision%20was%20due%20to%20the%20lapses%20in%20the%20signalling%20circuit%20alteration%20carried%20out%20at%20the%20North%20Signal%20Goomty%20(of%20the%20station)%20in%20the%20past%2C%20and%20during%20the%20execution%20of%20the%20signalling%20work%20related%20to%20replacement%20of%20Electric%20Lifting%20Barrier%20for%20level%20crossing%20gate%20no.%2094%20at%20the%20Station.%20These%20lapses%20resulted%20in%20wrong%20signalling%20to%20the%20Train%20No.%2012841%20wherein%20the%20UP%20Home%20Signal%20indicated%20a%20Green%20aspect%20for%20run-through%20movement%20on%20the%20UP%20main%20line%20of%20the%20station%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vaishnaw%20said%20in%20his%20written%20reply%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20the%20crossover%20connecting%20the%20UP%20main%20line%20to%20the%20UP%20loop%20line%20(crossover%2017%20A%2FB)%20was%20set%20to%20the%20UP%20loop%20line%3B%20the%20wrong%20signalling%20resulted%20in%20the%20Train%20No.%2012841%20traversing%20on%20the%20UP%20loop%20line%2C%20and%20eventual%20rear-collision%20with%20the%20Goods%20train%20(No.%20N%2FDDIP)%20standing%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Mukul%20Wasnik%20asked%20the%20government%20about%20the%20number%20of%20people%20who%20died%20and%20those%20who%20suffered%20injuries%20in%20the%20train%20accident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20railway%20minister%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C295%20passengers%20lost%20their%20lives%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E176%20sustained%20grievous%20injuries%2C%20451%20suffered%20simple%20injuries%20and%20180%20received%20first%20aid%20t%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3Ereatment%20and%20left.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft