2C%20the%20Indian%20film%20industry%20was%20dominated%20by%20Hindi-language%20movies%2C%20thus%20providing%20little%20to%20no%20opportunity%20for%20regional%20script%20movies.%20This%20spell%20ended%20in%201963%20with%20Kundan%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20Bhojpuri%20film%20%3Cem%3EGanga%20Maiya%20Tohe%20Piyari%20Chadhaibo%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ea%20poignant%20film%20on%20widow%20remarriage.%20In%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20a%20young%20film%20enthusiast%20Manu%20Nayak%20was%20so%20influenced%20by%20this%20that%20it%20compelled%20him%20to%20make%20a%20Chhattisgarhi%20film%20on%20a%20subject%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2Fweb-stories%2Flawyer-dedicated-two-decades-to-helping-inter-caste-couples-love-freely-live-safely%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20was%20passionate%20about%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20353px)%20100vw%2C%20353px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FManu-3-1689943324.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22353%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kahi%20Debe%20Sandesh%20faced%20major%20backlash%20following%20its%20release%20for%20shedding%20light%20on%20caste%20discrimination%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FManu-3-1689943324.jpg%20353w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FManu-3-1689943324-300x233.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FManu-3-1689943324-150x116.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324748%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22274%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKahi%20Debe%20Sandesh%20faced%20major%20backlash%20following%20its%20release%20for%20shedding%20light%20on%20caste%20discrimination%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20A%20photobook%20by%20Aayush%20Chandrawanshi%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3