rly%20to%20the%20masses%2C%20society%20would%20not%20progress.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%20intent%20on%20these%20issues%20seeing%20the%20light%20of%20day%2C%20Nayak%20began%20his%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F291630%2Fsanober-pardiwalla-bollywood-stuntwoman-for-actress-alia-bhatt-deepika-padukone-movies%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equest%20of%20casting%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20song%20recorded%20with%20legend%20Mohammed%20Rafi%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3EJhamkat%20nadiya%20bahini%20laage%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%94%20a%20quick%20casting%20of%20theatre%20actors%20who%20were%20willing%2C%20and%20a%20record%2022-day%20packed%20shoot%20schedule%2C%20%3Cem%3EKahi%20Debe%20Sandesh%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewas%20ready%20to%20roll.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Nayak%20says%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20spent%20the%20next%20two%20years%20paying%20off%20my%20debts.%20But%20I%20had%20the%20satisfaction%20of%20making%20the%20first%20Chhattisgarhi%20film.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F261909%2Findia-film-project-ritam-bhatanagar-asia-largest-film-festival-content-creators%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20film%3C%2Fa%3E%20continues%20to%20stand%20by%20its%20legacy%20of%20being%20among%20the%20first%20to%20shed%20light%20on%20caste%20discrimination.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20cinema%20has%20come%20a%20long%20way%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20narratives%20highlighted%20in%20caste%20movies%2C%20as%20Sanjiv%20Jaiswal%2C%20director%20of%20%3Cem%3EShudra%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2012)%20emphasised%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20%3Cem%3EOutlook%20India%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20dare%20to%20make%20films%20like%20these%20%5BShudra%5D%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20put%20the%20spotlight%20on%20the%20discriminated%20communities.%20There%20is%20a%20marked%20shift%20in%20how%20these%20movies%20are%20made%20today.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F256049%2Fdangal-to-baahubali-mumbai-artist-uses-mundane-items-to-create-magic-in-3000-movies%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20storylines%3C%2Fa%3E%20give%20the%20communities%20depicted%20greater%20agency%20and%20power%20over%20the%20story.%20This%20is%20a%20big%20change%20from%20the%20past%2C%20when%20either%20their%20entire%20existence%20would%20be%20ignored%2C%20or%20portrayed%20in%20poor%20light%2C%20causing%20more%20harm%20than%20good%20for%20these%20sections.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Divya%20Sethu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhomegrown.co.in%2Fhomegrown-creators%2Fhow-the-first-chhattisgarhi-film-tackled-casteism-in-the-1960s%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHow%20The%20First%20Chhattisgarhi%20Film%20Tackled%20Casteism%20In%20The%201960s%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Disha%20Bijolia%2C%20Published%20on%2020%20March%202023.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcaravanmagazine.in%2Ffilm%2Fhow-first-chhattisgarhi-film-questioned-caste%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMedium%20and%20the%20Message%20by%20Caravan%20Magazine%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Published%20on%202%20December%202022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fwhen-indira-saved-first-chhattisgarhi-film-from-ban%2Farticleshow%2F47102678.cms%5