0it%20was%20only%20in%202017%2C%20when%20it%20aligned%20with%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20that%20it%20got%20its%20first%20breakthrough%20and%20won%20four%20out%20of%20the%20eight%20seats%20it%20contested.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Rajbhar%20became%20a%20cabinet%20minister%20on%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20March%2019%2C%202017%2C%20in%20the%20Adityanath-led%20BJP%20government%2C%20though%20he%20was%20later%20sacked%20from%20the%20cabinet%20due%20to%20anti%20alliance%20activities.%20For%20the%202022%20assembly%20elections%20in%20the%20state%2C%20he%20aligned%20with%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20his%20party%20won%20six%20out%20of%20the%2017%20seats%20it%20contested.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJuly%2016%20saw%20Rajbhar%E2%80%99s%20return%20to%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%2C%20after%20months%20of%20speculation%20regarding%20his%20future%20plans%20since%20breaking%20up%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20last%20year.%20Rajbhar%20is%20known%20for%20his%20outspoken%20nature%20and%20in%20conversation%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20he%20covered%20future%20plans%2C%20his%20reasons%20for%20returning%20to%20the%20NDA%20after%20more%20than%20four%20years%2C%20his%20demands%20from%20the%20alliance%20and%20the%20future%20of%20his%20party%20legislator%20Abbas%20Ansari.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEdited%20excerpts%20follow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPeople%20want%20to%20know%20why%20you%20change%20parties%20repeatedly.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOm%20Prakash%20Rajbhar%20is%20a%20voice%20that%20constantly%20raises%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20oppressed%2C%20the%20marginalised%2C%20the%20Dalits%2C%20the%20backward%20and%20the%20minority%20communities%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20%E2%80%93%20both%20on%20the%20streets%20and%20in%20the%20assembly.%20SBSP%20%5Bthe%20acronym%20for%20his%20party%5D%20is%20always%20ready%20to%20align%20with%20any%20party%20that%20shares%20the%20goal%20of%20granting%20these%20communities%20their%20rights.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20primary%20objective%20of%20Om%20Prakash%20Rajbhar%E2%80%99s%20political%20career%20has%20been%20to%20ensure%20the%20rights%20of%20these%20people%2C%20and%20the%20fight%20will%20continue%20until%20they%20receive%20their%20due%20rights.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhether%20we%20remain%20in%20opposition%20or%20in%20power%2C%20if%20someone%20sees%20our%20struggle%20as%20%E2%80%9Cparty%20switching%2C%E2%80%9D%20that%20genuinely%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20bother%20us.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20changed%20since%20the%202022%20assembly%20elections%20that%20you%20were%20compelled%20to%20align%20with%20the%20same%20party%2C%20BJP%2C%20which%20you%20used%20to%20criticise%20and%20talked%20of%20removing%20from%20power%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20primary%20priority%20was%20to%20be%20in%20the%20opposition%2C%20and%20we%20do%20not%20deny%20that.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20that%20time%2C%20due%20to%20certain%20policies%20of%20the%20BJP%20that%20went%20against%20our%20principles%2C%20we%20were%20seen%20as%20making%20efforts%20to%20prevent%20them%20from%20coming%20into%20power%2C%20and%20we%20aligned%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party.%20However%2C%20it%20has%20been%20the%20SP%E2%80%99s%20history%20to%20deceive%20and%20exploit%20the%20oppressed%2C%20marginalised%2C%20Dalit%2C%20backward%2C%20and%20minority%20communities%20by%20simply%20taking%20their%20votes%20and%20focusing%20solely%20on%20the%20development%20of%20their%20own%20family%20and%20kin.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESocialism%20holds%20no%20significance%20for%20them.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConversely%2C%20the%20Bhartiya%20Janata%20Party%20understood%20the%20seriousness%20of%20our%20concerns%2C%20and%20keeping%20in%20mind%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20marginalised%20communities%2C%20the%20Dalits%2C%20the%20backward%20classes%2C%20and%20the%20minorities%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20they%20were%20willing%20to%20accept%20our%20demands.%20Due%20to%20this%2C%20we%20were%20ready%20to%20join%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20successful%20leadership%20of%20our%20honourable%20prime%20minister%20%5BNarendra%20Modi%5D%2C%20who%20raised%20the%20flag%20of%20India%20as%20a%20distinct%20entity%20in%20the%20world%20has%20also%20helped%20us%20in%20reaching%20our%20decision%20of%20joining%20the%20NDA.%20This%20fills%20all%20Indians%20with%20a%20sense%20of%20pride.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20numerous%20welfare%20schemes%20implemented%20in%20the%20country%20also%20contributed%20significantly%20to%20our%20decision%20of%20choosing%20the%20NDA%20over%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20do%20you%20think%20led%20to%20your%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20failure%20in%20the%202022%20elections%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%202022%20assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20SBSP%20formed%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20to%20work%20towards%20the%20welfare%20and%20rights%20of%20the%20oppressed%2C%20marginalised%2C%20Dalit%2C%20backward%2C%20and%20minority%20communities.%20Thanks%20to%20our%20alliance%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20went%20from%20winning%2047%20seats%20to%20111%20seats.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20after%20joining%20forces%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20we%20realised%20that%20while%20they%20talk%20about%20issues%20concerning%20Dalits%20and%20marginalised%20communities%2C%20they%20deceive%20people%20of%20these%20communities%20entirely.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20giving%20political%20representation%20and%20sharing%20power%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20sidelines%20these%20communities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20this%2C%20the%20SBSP%20faithfully%20followed%20the%20principles%20of%20the%20alliance%20and%20consistently%20tried%20to%20persuade%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20to%20understand%20the%20right%20perspectives.%20Unfortunately%2C%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20disregarded%20my%20advice%20%E2%80%93%20which%20looked%20at%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20oppressed%20and%20marginalised%20%E2%80%93%20and%20this%20led%20to%20the%20breakup%20of%20the%20alliance%20between%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20the%20SBSP.%20This%20incident%20clearly%20highlights%20that%20Samajwadi%20Party%20supremo%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20cannot%20tolerate%20valid%20criticism.%20The%20saying%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Emeetha-meetha%20gup-gup%2C%20kadwa-kadwa%20thoo-thoo%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(%E2%80%98when%20it%E2%80%99s%20sweet%2C%20eat%20it%2C%20when%20it%20is%20bitter%2C%20throw%20it)%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0fits%20this%20situation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21185744%2FScreenshot-2023-07-21-at-6.57.09.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21185744%2FScreenshot-2023-07-21-at-6.57.09.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21185744%2FScreenshot-2023-07-21-at-6.57.09-300x144.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21185744%2FScreenshot-2023-07-21-at-6.57.09-1024x492.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-664435%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22576%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAkhilesh%20Yadav%20and%20O.P.%20Rajbhar.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40VishvanathYad11%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAkhilesh%20Yadav%20also%20talks%20about%20the%20PDA%20%5Ban%20acronym%20for%20%3Cem%3Epichre%3C%2Fem%3E%20(backward)%2C%20Dalit%20and%20%3Cem%3Ealpashankhak%3C%2Fem%3E%20(minority)%5D%2C%20which%20can%20be%20seen%20as%20addressing%20the%20concerns%20of%20marginalised%20communities.%20What%20is%20your%20opinion%20on%20this%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAkhilesh%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20mention%20of%20PDA%20is%20merely%20a%20deceptive%20tactic.%20He%20is%20deceiving%20the%20people%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20attempting%20to%20mislead%20them.%20It%20is%20an%20attempt%20to%20deceive%20the%20people%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20especially%20the%20marginalised%20communities.%20If%20anyone%20has%20deceived%20and%20cheated%20the%20backward%20classes%2C%20Dalits%2C%20and%20minorities%20the%20most%2C%20it%20is%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAkhilesh%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20PDA%20slogan%20will%20ultimately%20be%20exposed%20as%20a%20hollow%20promise%2C%20and%20in%20the%20upcoming%202024%20elections%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20will%20completely%20reject%20his%20bicycle%20symbol.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20had%20taken%20a%20strong%20stand%20on%20caste-based%20Census.%20Will%20your%20stance%20remain%20the%20same%20even%20after%20aligning%20with%20the%20BJP%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20have%20been%20advocating%20for%20a%20caste-based%20Census%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESamajik%20Nyay%20Samiti%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%5Ba%20social%20justice%20committee%5D%20for%20the%20past%2020%20years.%20The%20demand%20for%20free%20and%20uniform%20education%2C%20and%20free%20healthcare%2C%20has%20been%20my%20consistent%20stand%20for%20the%20past%2020%20years.%20The%20stand%20of%20the%20SBSP%20will%20remain%20the%20same%20as%20it%20has%20been%20before.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20now%20that%20we%20are%20a%20part%20of%20the%20NDA%2C%20we%20will%20discuss%20these%20issues%20with%20all%20the%20constituent%20and%20allied%20parties%20of%20the%20NDA%20in%20order%20to%20address%20them%20in%20the%20future.%20But%20the%20SBSP%20will%20continue%20to%20push%20for%20the%20caste-based%20Census%20and%20the%20Samiti%2C%20which%20have%20been%20our%20party%E2%80%99s%20demands%20from%20the%20beginning.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDara%20Singh%20Chauhan%20has%20rejoined%20the%20party%20now%20that%20you%20have%20returned%20to%20your%20old%20alliance.%20Are%20we%20going%20to%20see%20more%20people%20joining%20soon%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESamajwadi%20Party%20talks%20of%20PDA%C2%A0and%20in%20Dara%20Singh%20Chauhan%E2%80%99s%20return%20to%20BJP%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20has%20lost%20its%20first%20PDA%20wicket.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20way%20the%20SP%20talks%20about%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESavarnas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20gives%20the%20impression%20that%20they%20do%20not%20desire%20the%20votes%20of%20the%20upper%20caste%20community.%20In%20such%20a%20scenario%2C%20upper%20caste%20people%20within%20the%20SP%20should%20distance%20themselves%20from%20the%20party.%20In%20the%20future%2C%20many%20leaders%20and%20legislators%20within%20the%20SP%20will%20bid%20farewell%20to%20the%20party%2C%20just%20like%20Dara%20Singh%20Chauhan%20did.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20did%20you%20discuss%20during%20your%20meeting%20with%20Amit%20Shah%3F%20What%20strategy%20will%20your%20alliance%20adopt%20for%20the%202024%20elections%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20were%20open%20and%20frank%20discussions%20with%20the%20honourable%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E.%20There%20was%20agreement%20on%20several%20issues%2C%20and%20there%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20discussions%20and%20consensus%20on%20various%20matters%20in%20the%20future%20as%20well.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20for%20the%20strategy%20for%20the%202024%20elections%2C%20let%20it%20remain%20a%20strategy.%20However%2C%20let%20me%20say%20that%20due%20to%20the%20alliance%20of%20the%20SBSP%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20opposition%20has%20nothing%20left%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20In%20the%202024%20elections%2C%20SBSP-BJP%20will%20secure%20victory%20on%20all%2080%20seats%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20under%20the%20successful%20leadership%20of%20the%20honourable%20Prime%20Minister%20of%20India%20Shri%20Narendra%20Modi%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Narendra%20Modi%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20will%20become%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20India%20for%20the%20third%20consecutive%20term.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConsidering%20that%20you%20have%20emphasised%20on%20social%20justice%20and%20the%20fight%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20marginalised%20communities%2C%20and%20have%20spoken%20against%20the%20BJP%20on%20these%20issues%2C%20are%20you%20now%20confident%20that%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20marginalised%20and%20oppressed%20will%20be%20honoured%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYes%2C%20I%20reaffirm%20that%20I%20have%20previously%20stated%20that%20during%20our%20%5Bparty%20national%20chief%20secretary%20Arvind%20Rajbhar%20and%20O.P.%20Rajbhar%5D%20meeting%20with%20the%20honourable%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20there%20were%20discussions%20as%20well%20as%20agreement%20on%20various%20matters.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETherefore%2C%20it%20is%20evident%20that%20in%20the%20future%2C%20the%20ongoing%20fight%20of%20the%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party%20for%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20marginalised%20communities%2C%20including%20Dalits%2C%20backward%20classes%2C%20and%20minorities%2C%20will%20continue.%20Whether%20it%20is%20about%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESamajik%20Nyay%20Samiti%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20inclusion%20of%20Bhar-Rajbhar%20caste%20in%20the%20Scheduled%20list%2C%20or%20the%20issue%20of%20caste-based%20Census%2C%20we%20are%20fully%20assured%20that%20our%20demands%20will%20be%20heard%20and%20fulfilled.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Pramod%20Tiwari%20has%20said%20that%20no%20one%20can%20guess%20where%20you%20are%20today%20and%20where%20you%20will%20be%20tomorrow.%20How%20would%20you%20respond%20to%20this%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20not%20even%20talk%20about%20Pramod%20Tiwari.%20Coming%20to%20Congress%2C%20the%20party%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20presence%20as%20far%20as%20UP%20is%20concerned.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECongress%2C%20despite%20being%20a%20national%20party%2C%20has%20become%20insignificant%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20compared%20to%20the%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party.%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party%20holds%20a%20greater%20number%20of%20MLAs%20than%20Congress.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETherefore%2C%20Pramod%20Tiwari%E2%80%99s%20statement%20only%20confirms%20that%20Congress%20has%20completely%20lost%20its%20ground%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20It%20is%20evident%20that%20many%20Congress%20leaders%20are%20making%20such%20statements%20due%20to%20their%20own%20perplexity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21184629%2FFzx5rO4aMAEGpvw.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21184629%2FFzx5rO4aMAEGpvw.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21184629%2FFzx5rO4aMAEGpvw-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21184629%2FFzx5rO4aMAEGpvw-1024x769.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-664433%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22901%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECongress%E2%80%99s%20Pramod%20Tiwari.%