nsensus%20will%20be%20reached%20on%20them.%20Therefore%2C%20when%20there%20is%20consensus%20on%20issues%2C%20there%20is%20no%20question%20of%20leaving%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20alliance.%20Those%20who%20are%20making%20such%20statements%20are%20completely%20unsettled%20by%20the%20alliance%20between%20the%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party.%20They%20are%20starting%20to%20see%20their%20own%20defeat%20even%20before%20it%20happens.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20many%20seats%20do%20you%20expect%20your%20party%20to%20get%20in%20the%20coalition%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20there%20is%20a%20consensus%20on%20several%20key%20issues%20and%20agreements%20have%20been%20reached%2C%20the%20allocation%20of%20seats%20becomes%20less%20significant.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20worth%20noting%20that%20the%20inclusion%20of%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party%20in%20the%20alliance%20with%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20carries%20its%20own%20importance.%20The%20allocation%20of%20seats%20is%20a%20mere%20formality%2C%20and%20the%20final%20decision%20regarding%20seats%20will%20be%20made%20through%20discussions%20between%20our%20leadership%20and%20the%20top%20leadership%20of%20BJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWill%20all%20the%20leaders%20of%20your%20party%20also%20be%20part%20of%20the%20NDA%3F%20Including%20Abbas%20Ansari%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20no%20specific%20individual%20from%20our%20party%20has%20joined%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance.%20The%20coalition%20formed%20is%20between%20the%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20the%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party%20has%20become%20a%20part%20of%20the%20NDA.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20for%20Abbas%20Ansari%2C%20he%20was%20part%20of%20the%20coalition%20between%20the%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party%20and%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20during%20the%202022%20state%20assembly%20elections.%20Under%20that%20coalition%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20fielded%2012%20candidates%20on%20the%20symbol%20of%20the%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party.%20Upholding%20the%20principles%20of%20coalition%20unity%2C%20we%20supported%20those%20candidates%20under%20the%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party%20symbol.%20Abbas%20Ansari%20is%20one%20of%20those%20candidates.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%20Abbas%20Ansari%20has%20to%20decide%20whether%20he%20will%20remain%20with%20us%20or%20decides%20to%20go.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShould%20we%20now%20consider%20this%20as%20O.P.%20Rajbhar%E2%80%99s%20final%20decision%3F%20Will%20SBSP%20now%20continue%20to%20be%20with%20the%20BJP%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECurrently%2C%20we%20are%20a%20part%20of%20the%20NDA.%20It%20has%20been%20the%20history%20of%20the%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party%20that%20whenever%20we%20have%20been%20in%20an%20alliance%2C%20we%20have%20remained%20steadfast%20and%20committed%20to%20it%20with%20full%20strength%20and%20honesty.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWould%20you%20like%20to%20share%20your%20hopes%20regarding%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20alliance%20between%20the%20Suheldev%20Bharatiya%20Samaj%20Party%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20has%20ensured%20that%20there%20is%20no%20opposition%20left%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20In%20the%20upcoming%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20all%20the%20NDA%20will%20work%20together%20to%20win%20all%2080%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20With%20even%20more%20seats%20than%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20we%20will%20secure%20a%20massive%20majority%20and%20ensure%20the%20formation%20of%20a%20government%20and%20contribute%20in%20putting%20honourable%20Prime%20Minister%20Shri%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20office%