0she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20the%20play%20elements%20you%20see%20on%20playgrounds%20built%20by%20Anthill%20like%20octopus%2C%20elephants%20or%20horses%20came%20from%20children.%20Other%20children%20wanted%20a%20rocket%20in%20their%20playground.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20tried%20to%20incorporate%20some%20of%20those%20major%20structural%20designs%2C%20but%20also%20keep%20activities%20in%20mind%20when%20we%20were%20designing%20those%20final%20elements.%20It%20took%20a%20lot%20of%20iterations.%20Not%20all%20of%20our%20design%20elements%20became%20successful%20in%20the%20first%20go%2C%20but%20we%20seek%20to%20ensure%20a%20constant%20feedback%20loop%20that%20happened.%20We%20still%20engage%20in%20these%20processes%2C%20but%20today%20we%20have%20around%20100%20different%20designs%20in%20our%20design%20library%20although%20we%20still%20take%20requests%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Rai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20we%E2%80%99re%20operating%20at%20a%20much%20larger%20scale%20today%2C%20we%20have%20this%20written%20site%20survey%20form%20that%20either%20we%20fill%20when%20we%20visit%20a%20site%20or%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20local%20community%20or%20a%20teacher%20who%20fills%20it%20out%20for%20us.%20That%20basically%20captures%20what%20children%20need%20and%20if%20there%20is%20anything%20in%20specific%20that%20like%20that%20particular%20community%20or%20school%20wants%20to%20do%2C%20we%20look%20at%20our%20design%20library%20and%20see%20what%20fits%20well%20into%20this%20playground.%20We%20try%20to%20leave%20some%20space%20for%20designing%20new%20elements%20as%20well%20because%20we%20want%20to%20give%20some%20unique%20touch%20to%20most%20of%20our%20playgrounds%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20756px)%20100vw%2C%20756px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FPretend-play-elements-Elephant-168