n%20of%20these%20kids.%20But%20I%20am%20looking%20at%20prospective%20schools%20which%20can%20take%20them%20in%20when%20they%20will%20need%20secondary%20education%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSelf-doubts%20keep%20bothering%20me%2C%20but%20what%20keeps%20me%20going%20is%20the%20smile%20on%20all%20these%20little%20faces.%20These%20children%20are%20so%20untouched%20and%20pure.%20I%20believe%20that%20I%20am%20just%20a%20medium%2C%20and%20it%20was%20the%20fate%20of%20these%20kids%20that%20brought%20me%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20850px)%20100vw%2C%20850px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-7-1689774500.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Portia%20with%20the%20kids%20she%20teaches%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22850%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-7-1689774500.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-7-1689774500-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-7-1689774500-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-7-1689774500-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fkomic-school-7-1689774500-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324420%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22444%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20children%20in%20her%20boarding%20school%20are%20in%20the%20age%20group%20of%208%20to%2010%20years.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Portia%20Putatunda%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20her%20journey%20of%20healing%20from%20her%20father%E2%80%99s%20loss%20so%20far%2C%20Portia%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20had%20my%20fair%20share%20of%20low%20moments%20in%20life.%20There