3EGautam%20Trivedi%20(26)%2C%20a%20Vadodara%20resident%20and%20music%20producer%20by%20profession%2C%20wanted%20to%20grow%20his%20own%20vegetables.%20After%20receiving%20training%20from%20Shashank%2C%20he%20set%20up%20an%20aquaponics%20farm%20in%20a%2050%20sq%20ft%20area%20of%20his%20garden.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20an%20aquaponics%20set%20up%2C%20we%20get%20nice%20green%20leafy%20vegetables%20that%20are%20crunchier%20and%20better%20in%20taste%20than%20that%20available%20in%20the%20market.%20It%20also%20requires%20low%20maintenance%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20he%20has%20trained%2035%20people%20from%20Gujarat%20and%20Rajasthan%20through%20offline%20and%20online%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20one-to-one%20process.%20I%20conduct%20a%20six-hour%20class.%20In%20the%20initial%20three%20hours%2C%20I%20inform%20them%20about%20the%20different%20plants%20that%20a%20farmer%20can%20grow.%20In%20the%20next%20three%20hours%2C%20I%20train%20them%20on%20how%20to%20implement%20the%20aquaponics%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shashank%2C%20who%20charges%20Rs%202%2C500%20and%20Rs%203%2C000%20for%20offline%20and%20online%20classes%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20a%20few%20tips%20on%20aquaponics%20farming%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CCrops%20require%20an%20environment%20with%20the%20optimal%20temperature.%20For%20instance%2C%20to%20grow%20leafy%20vegetables%2C%20a%20temperature%20between%2025%20and%2030%20degrees%20Celsius%20is%20needed.%20Whereas%20for%20hilly%20crops%2C%20such%20as%20strawberries%2C%20you%20need%20to%20reduce%20the%20temperature%20to%2018%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20and%20for%20crops%20like%20lettuce%2C%20up%20to%2015%20degrees%20Celsius.%20We%20use%20urban%20clay%20pots%20to%20regulate%20the%20temperature%20of%20water%20in%20the%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faquaponics-1689666293.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shashank%20says%20it%20costs%20Rs%20800%20per%20sq%20ft%20to%20establish%20an%20aquaponics%20terrace%20farm%20in%20a%20vertical%20setup.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faquaponics-1689666293.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faquaponics-1689666293-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faquaponics-1689666293-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faquaponics-1689666293-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faquaponics-1689666293-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324146%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShashank%20says%20it%20costs%20Rs%20800%20per%20sq%20ft%20to%20establish%20an%20aquaponics%20terrace%20farm%20in%20a%20vertical%20setup.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20this%2C%20he%20suggests%20farmers%20introduce%20fish%20like%20gold%20and%20koi%20fish.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20produce%20more%20excreta%20and%20also%20survive%20in%20harsh%20temperature%20conditions.%20Just%20ensure%20to%20filter%20the%20water%20before%20adding%20the%20fish%20to%20the%20tank%3B%20water%20should%20not%20be%20hard.%20You%20can%20add%20150%20fish%20in%20a%201%2C000-litre%20tank.%20For%20edible%20fish%2C%20you%20would%20require%20a%20tank%20of%203%2C000%20litres%20as%20their%20size%20grows%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShashank%20says%20it%20costs%20Rs%20800%20per%20sq%20ft%20to%20establish%20an%20aquaponics%20terrace%20farm%20in%20a%20vertical%20setup.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20cost%20can%20be%20reduced%20to%20Rs%20400%20if%20farmers%20wish%20to%20avoid%20vertical%20farming.%20It%20is%20a%20one-time%20investment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFood%20production%20is%20basic%20yet%20urban%20residents%20avert%20from%20the%20idea.%20Instead%20of%20earning%20a%20good%20income%20for%20myself%2C%20my%20focus%20is%20on%20enabling%20urban%20Indians%20to%20grow%20their%20own%20vegetables%20even%20if%20they%20have%20a%20small%20space%20%E2%80%94%20as%20small%20as%20one%20square%20foot%2C%20The%20aquaponics%20farming%20will%20enable%20people%20to%20decentralise%20food%20production%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shashank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIf%20you%20wish%20to%20learn%20aquaponics%20farming%2C%20you%20can%20contact%20Shashank%20at%20%2B91%2099742%2004501.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689687228000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Faquaponics-2-1689666156.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D324007%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Vadodara-resident%20Shashank%20Chaubey%20quit%20his%20comfortable%20job%20to%20grow%20vegetables%20using%20aquaponics%20farming.%20Having%20started%20with%20zero%20farming%20experience%2C%20today%20he%20grows%202%2C500%20varieties%20of%20plants%20on%20a%202%2C000%20sq%20ft%20commercial%20terrace%20farm%20and%20helps%20other%20people%20do%20the%20same.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324007%2Fvadodara-engineer-quit-job-to-grow-vegetables-at-home-terrace-aquaponics-farming%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Forgotten%20Indian%20Who%20Made%20Nobel%20Laureate%20Ronald%20Ross%E2%80%99%20Malaria%20Breakthrough%20Possible%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20speak%20of%20the%20role%20of%20Indian%20men%20and%20women%20in%20shaping%20the%20medical%20world%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener