ped%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F270232%2Fbest-biryani-places-in-india-iconic-restaurants%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELucknowi%20biryani%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20he%20came%20to%20Kolkata.%20With%20the%20introduction%20of%20potatoes%2C%20it%20became%20what%20we%20today%20relish%20as%20Kolkata%20biryani%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2055-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20that%20time%2C%20potatoes%20were%20considered%20a%20%3Cem%3Enayab%3C%2Fem%3E%20(exotic)%20delicacy.%20Although%20common%20people%20could%20not%20afford%20them%2C%20the%20vegetable%20was%20introduced%20in%20the%20royal%20kitchens.%20%E2%80%9CSince%20it%20has%20the%20capacity%20to%20absorb%20all%20aromas%20of%20spices%2C%20it%20enhances%20the%20flavours%20when%20it%E2%80%99s%20added%20to%20the%20dish.%20It%20was%20readily%20accepted%20by%20the%20King%20and%20the%20people.%20After%20his%20death%2C%20when%20his%20%3Cem%3Emulazim%3C%2Fem%3Es%20(workers)%20were%20jobless%2C%20they%20went%20to%20cities%20and%20this%20biryani%20was%20spread%20in%20Kolkata%20city%20and%20became%20popular%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manzilat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCiUaf9mt1qC%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCiUaf9mt1qC%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3